src: sita kuvikela kuphela kwemanti more matshediso litiko letemanti ne kutfutfwa kwelindle (idws) lisebentisana nelidolobha lasekapa kuphungula lesomiso lesisenshonalaga kapa, lekungulesibi kakhulu kunalesake saba khona eminyakeni lelishumi.
tgt: thusa go thibelwe letsatsi la tlhokagalo ya metsi more matshediso efapha la metsi le kge leloleswe (dws) le di risana le ba toropokgolo ya kapa go namola leuba kwa kapa bokone, leuba le le masisi le le iseng le bonwe mo dingwa geng di le lesome.

src: ngekusho kwedws imvula ayikani ngalokwanele kantsi emazinga emadamu ehlile.
tgt: go ya ka ba dws ga go dipula tse di lekaneng tse di neleng mme seelo sa metsi mo matamong se wetse tlase.

src: loku kuphocelele labaphetse kutsi babeke imitsetfo lecinile kute kutsi emanti angapheli ngekushesha, lapho kutawuba bete emanti etimpompini.
tgt: seno se gapeleditse bothati go tlhagisa dikgato tse di gagamet seng go diegisa kgonagalo ya tl hokagalo ya metsi, fa dithepe di kgala metsi.

src: lidolobha lasekapa litawungenisa imikhawulo yelizinga 6b.
tgt: toropokgolo ya kapa e diragatsa legato la selekanyetso sa 6b.

src: loku kusho kutsi kutawuba nemkhawulo welusuku longemalitha la50 emanti noma nga phansi umuntfu ngamunye, noma ngabe kusekhaya, emsebentini, esikolweni noma kuphi kulenye indzawo.
tgt: seno se raya gore motho a le mongwe o na le tiriso ya selekanyetso sa letsatsi sa dilitara tsa metsi di le 50 kgotsa kwa tlase, e ka tswa e le kwa gae, tirong, sekolong kgotsa gongwe le gongwe.

src: ngalesikhatsi lelidolobha licondzise yonkhe imitamo yalo yekuvikela kuphela kwemanti, litsi lidzinga kutilungiselela simo lapho khona lingakhona kulawula lokwetfulwa kwemanti kulelidolobha kudzimate kufike busika.
tgt: fa toropokgolo e ntse e tsepa misitse maiteko otlhe a yona mo go thibeleng letsatsi la tlhokaga lo ya metsi, ya re e tshwanela go nna e ipaakanyeditse maemo ao a tla e kgontshang go laola metsi a yona le go a lelefatsa go fitlha setlha sa mariga se goroga.

src: "sitawuvala kutfunyelwa kwemanti etimpompini uma ngabe emadamu etfu afinyelela ezingeni lelingemaphesenti langu13.5.
tgt: "re tla tswala metsi a a yang kwa dithepeng fa matamo a rona otlhe a fitlha go seelo sa dipere sente di le 13.5. fa fela seelo sa matamo se fitlha go diperesente di le 13.5, ba tla simolola go tswala dipeipe tsa metsi, ntle le mo ma felong a a botlhokwa a kgwebo le mo ditheong tse di jaaka maokelo, go rialo toropokgolo mo polelo e ba e ba e dirileng.

src: uma ngabe emazinga emadamu sekakumaphesenti langu13.5, sitawucala kuvala loluhlelo lwekutfumela emanti etimpompini, ngaphandle kwetindzawo letibalulekile temabhizinisi netikhungo, letinjengetibhedlela," kusho lelidolobha ngesitatimende.
tgt: fela fa seno se simolola go di ragala, baagi ba tla bona metsi mo mafelong a go gelela metsi go ralala toropokgolo.

src: uma loku kwenteka, emanti bantfu batawalandza etindzaweni letibekiwe kulo lonkhe lelidolobha.
tgt: moagi a le mongwe o tla neelwa dilitara di le 25 tsa metsi ka letsatsi.

src: umuntfu ngamunye utawunikwa emalitha lange25 ngelilanga.
tgt: toropokgolo e simolotse ka tik watikwe e e dirang ka tiragalo tsa matlhotlhapelo (doc) go diraga tsa leano la matlhotlhapelo a a tlholwang ke metsi le le tla diraga diwang fa go ka tlhokagala metsi.

src: lelidolobha livule tikhungo talo letisebenta ngetinhlekelele (idoc) kutsi ticale luhlelo lwewater disaster plan, lelitawucala kusebenta uma ngabe kwenteka kutsi kuphele emanti.
tgt: didiba tse di borilweng toropokgolo ga e rotloetse tiriso ya didiba tse di borilweng tse di kwa ntle ga dikago mme ya re go nosetsa ka metsi a tsona go tla beelwa selekanyetso sa ura e le nngwe fela ka bolabobedi le bolamatlhatso, pele ga 9am le morago ga 6pm.

src: emabhulomashinilelidolobha alikukhutsati nakancane lokusetjentiswa kwemabulomashini lagujwa ngaphandle kantsi litsi kutselela kutawufinyetwa kube sikhatsi lesingandluli lihora linye kuphela ngabolesibili nangemgcibelo, ngembi kwensimbi ye9 ekuseni nangemuva kwensimbi ye6 ntsambama.
tgt: "tiriso ya metsi a a tswang mo didibeng tse di borilweng /petseng e tshwanetse e nne le mmetara mme botlhe ba ba a di risang ba tshwanetse go tshola direkoto mme ba di tlhagise ka nako ya fa go tlhatlhobiwa", toropokgolo e rialo.

src: "ibhulomashini/indzawo lengumtfombo wemanti kufanele ikalwe kantsi bonkhe labayisebentisako kufanele bagcine emarekhodi futsi agcinwe kwentelwa kuhlolwa," kusho lelidolobha.
tgt: e tlaleleditse ka gore baagi ba tshwanetse go bona tetla go tswa go dws fa ba rata go reki sa kgotsa go reka metsi a sediba se se borilweng/petse.

src: lichubeke latsi bantfu labahlala khona kufanele batfole imvume kadws uma ngabe bafuna kutsenga noma kutsengisa emanti emabhulomashini/indzawo lengumtfombo wemanti.
tgt: jaaka karolo ya maiteko a puso go laola tiriso ya metsi, dws e ne ya re bothati bo diragatsa dikgato tse di gagametseng go bona seelo se se lekanyedits weng sa metsi se obamelwa.

src: njengencenye yemitamo yahulumende yekulawula kusetjentiswa kwemanti, idws itse labaphetse basebentisa tindlela leticinile kute bacinisekise kwekutsi lemitsetfo lecinile lebekiwe yekwabelwa kwemanti iyalandzelelwa.
tgt: toropokgolo e dirisana le ba ti ragatso ya molao le ba yuniti ya dipatlisiso tse di kgethegileng (special investigating unit) go diragatsa kobamelo ya seleka nyetso sa metsi.

src: lelidolobha lisebenta nelicembu lebemtsetfo nelitsimba lebaphenyi lelikhetsekile kucinisekisa kuhambisana nemtsetfo.
tgt: go tsaya dikgato kgatlhanong le batlolamolao lefapha le sa tswa go dira ka tshwaraganelo le toropokgolo le tsepile mo ditiragalong tse di seng mo molaong tse di maleba na le metsi kwa mfuleni.

src: kutsatsa tinyatselo ngekumelana nalabaphula umtsetfo lelitiko lisandza kwenta umtamo ngekubambisana nalelidolobha, libukete ekusetjentisweni kwemanti ngendlela lengafanele endzaweni yasemfuleni.
tgt: maikaelelo e le go rarabolola ditiragalo tsotlhe tsa go se obamele kgotsa go se diragatse selekanyetso se se beilweng sa metsi, segolobogolo mafelo a go tlhatswa dijanaga a a seng ka fa molaong.

src: lenchubo ihlose kucondzisa konkhe kungasebentiseki kahle kwemanti nekungahambisani nalomtsetfo wekusebentisa emanti ngendlela lebekiwe, bebabukete ikakhulukati kuletindzawo letiwasha timoto letingekho emtsetfweni.
tgt: "go ya ka legato la toropok golo la selekanyetso sa 6b, metsi a mmasepala a a leng mo metemeng e mennye ga a ne a dirisediwa go tlhatswa dikoloi.

src: "ngekwemikhawulo yalelidolobha yemazinga 6b, la manti ladlekako (lanatsekako) amasipala angeke asetjentiselwa kuwasha timoto.
tgt: mafelo a a seng mo molaong a a tlhatswang dikoloi a dirisa met si a le mantsi.

src: tindzawo tekuwasha timoto letingekho emtsetfweni tidla emanti lamanyenti.
tgt: palo ya beng ba mafelo a a go tlhatswa dikoloi ba dirisa dipeipi tse di ikemet seng mo dikgwebong tsa bona, mme ba bangwe ba dirisa metsi go tswa mo dithepeng" go rialo lefapha.

src: banini betindzawo tekuwasha timoto letinyenti basebentisa emaphayiphi latimele kuhambisa ibhizinisi yabo, kantsi labanye basebentisa emanti lavela etimpompini," kusho lelitiko.
tgt: le fa go le dikemedi di le dintsi tse di boineelo tse di dirang ka metsi, go thusa go efoga le tsatsi la tlhokagalo ya metsi, toropokgolo e dirile boikuelo mo baaging ba yona go nna le seabe mo go somareleng metsi.

src: noma bakhona labangemancusa emanti labatinikele labasebentela kusita kuvikela kuphela kwemanti, lelidolobha licela bantfu balo kutsi nabo badlale indzima yabo ekongeni emanti.
tgt: "re tlhoka botlhe ba ba di risang metsi go ikamaganya le maiteko a setlhopha sa toro pokgolo ya kapa," go rialo mot latsammeyara wa toropokgolo ya kapa ian neilson.

src: "sicela bonkhe labasebentisa emanti kutsi bangenelele kulomtamo welidolobha laseka pa," kusho lisekela sodolobha wasekapa ian neilson.
tgt: maele a go somarela metsi tswala thepe fa o tlhapa meno, o beola kgotsa o tshasa sesepa mo diatleng.

src: emasu ekonga emanti vala impompi ngalesikhatsi ugeza ematinyo, ushefa noma ufaka insipho etandleni shawa sikhashana kantsi usebentise emanti lamancane nawugeza vikela kutsenga emanti lasemabhodleleni.
tgt: dirisa šawara go tlhapa mme o dirise metsi a mannye fa o tlhapa.

src: imoto washa imoto yakho ngelibhakede nesipontshi kuphela.
tgt: koloi dirisa kgamelo le sepontšhe fela go tlhatswa koloi.

src: esigezelweni shawa kunekusebentisa libhavu sebentisa emanti lamancane ebhavini gezisani bantfwana labancane ndzawonye flashani emathoyilethi uma ngabe sekunuka kakhulu beka sitini kucistern yakho kwehlisa lizinga lekusebenta kwemanti.
tgt: phaposi ya go tlhapa šawara mo boemong ba go dirisa bata go tlhapa.

src: likhishi sebentisa izinki levaliwe uma uwasha titja, kunekutsi uwavulele aphume sebentisa insipho yekuwasha titja ibe yincane, ehlisa sidzingo sekutipula vala izinki ngalesikhatsi uwasha tibhidvo, kunekutsi uwavulele aphume sebentisa lamanti lowashe ngawo titselo netibhidvo kutselela timbali.
tgt: dirisa metsi a mannye fa o dirisa bata go tlhapa.

src: buka imitha yemanti ngembi nangemuva kwemahora lamabili, uma ngabe ningakaze nisebentise emanti.
tgt: folaša metsi a a mo ntlwaneng fela fa go utlwala monkgo.

src: uma ngabe lemitha ayisafani nasekucaleni, kusho kutsi kukhona lapho kuvuta khona.
tgt: baya setena ka fa gare ga sisitene go fokotsa tiriso ya metsi.

src: takhamuti tiyacelwa kutsi tilungise timpompi letivutako.
tgt: boapelo tswala sinki fa o tlhatswa dijana, o se tlogele metsi a elela go tswa mo thepeng.

src: impompi levuta ngelitfonsi linye ngelisekhondi imosha emalitha lalinganiselwa ku10 220 emanti ngemnyaka.
tgt: dirisa sesepa se le sennye fela sa go tlhatswa dijana, gore o seka wa pateletsega go di tsokotsa.

src: tfola emandla akho futsi, bika kudlwengulwa adele schormann kuba ngulohluku nyetwe ngetemacansi noma udlwengulwe kuyintfo lebuhlungu kakhulu le umuntfu angabukana nayo.
tgt: tsaya maatla a gago, bega petelelo adele schormann go nna motswasetlha belo wa tshotlakako ka thobalano kgotsa petelelo ke nngwe ya maite mogelo a a maswe a motho a ka lebaganang le ona.

src: kungako emaphoyisa aseningizimu afrika (isaps) abe netinhlelo lebatilungisako kwenta kube lula futsi kuphephe kutsi bantfu bakhone kubika lobugebengu.
tgt: ke ka fao tirelo ya sepodisi sa aforikaborwa (saps) e dirisang tsamaiso eo e dirang gore go nne bonolo ebile go sireletsegile go batho go ka bega bosenyi jono.

src: sikhulumeli semaphoyisa ase mpumalanga colonel mtsholi bhembe utsi kubalulekile kutsi umphakatsi usebentisane nemaphoyisa babike ngalobugebengu.
tgt: sebui sa sepodisi sa kwa mpumalanga mokolonele mtsholi bhembe o rile go botlhokwa gore baagi ba dirisane le sepodisi le go bega bosenyi jono.

src: "njengemaphoyisa, kungumsebenti wetfu kudlala indzi ma lenkhulu ekucinisekiseni kwekutsi labenta lobugebengu bayabanjwa nalabo labahlukumetekile baphatseke kahle.
tgt: "rona, jaaka re le ba sepodisi, ke tiro ya rona go nna le seabe se segolo go netefatsa fa batlolamola ba tlhagelela fa pele ga kgotla le go bona batswasetlhabelo ba nna ba bolokesegile.

src: sice la umphakatsi kutsi ute utobika emacala ekudlwengulwa esiteshini semaphoyisa lesisedvute nabo," kusho bhembe.
tgt: re rotloetsa baagi go tlhagelela le go bega dikgetse tsa petelelo kwa diteišeneng tsa sepodise tse di gaufi le bona," o rialo bhembe.

src: labahlukunyetiwe kufanele babike bugebengu bekuhluku nyetwa ngetemacansi emaphoyiseni kungakandluli emahora lange72 ngemuva kwekutsi kwenteke lobugebengu.
tgt: batswasetlhabelo ba tshwanetse go begela sepodisi ditiragalo tseno tsa bosenyi ba thobalano mo diureng di le 72 tsa tiragalo ya bosenyi jono.

src: bhembe ucwayise labahluku nyetwe ngekudlwengulwa kutsi batfole lusito lwabochwephesha labacwayisa ngetinhlungu ngemuva kwalesehlakalo.
tgt: bhembe o ne a eletsa batswasetlhabelo ba petelelo go bona thuso ya thitibatsomaikutlo ya morago ga go welwa ke setlhogo seno.

src: utsi, "ungahle utive ungcolile ufune kugeza emahlandla lambalwa kantsi ungatfuka wesabe kuphumela ngaphandle.
tgt: "o ka bona e kete o leswe mme wa batla go tlhapagangwe le gape mme e bile o ka nna ka letshogo le go tshaba go tswela kwa ntle.

src: akukho nakunye kwaloku lokungakajwayeleki noma kungatsi akusikahle.
tgt: ga go epe ya tsibogelo eo e e sa tlwaelegang.

src: kufanele ukhumbule kwekutsi kunetinsita letikhona kutsi tikusite".
tgt: o tshwanetse ka metlha o gakologelwe gore go ditirelo tse di leng gone tse di ka go thusang, " o rialo.

src: igreater rape intervention project (grip) ingulenye yetinhlangano letisita labahlukunyetwe ngekudlwengulwa kutsi bahlolelwe ligciwane lesandvulelangculazi nengculazi (ihiv/aids) naletinye tifo.
tgt: porojeke ya greater rape intervention (grip) ke nngwe ya ditheo tse di thusang batswasetlhabelo ba petelelo go dira diteko tsa hiv/aids le tsa malwetse mangwe.

src: sonhlalakahle wegrip thandiwe maseko utsi lenhlangano inakekela labahlukunyetwe ngekudlwengulwa.
tgt: modirediloago wa grip thandiwe maseko a re setheo se tlhokomela batswasetlhabelo ba petelelo.

src: utsi, "sibaniketa umgodla wekubanakekela bese laba la bahlukunyetiwe bahlala endlini yetfu yekuphepha badzimate balungele kukhuluma.
tgt: "re tlamela ka sephuthelwa na sa thuso le go letla motswa setlhabelo go nna mo ntlong e e bolokesegileng go fitlha a kgona go bua.

src: sinabochwephesha labahambembili labanakekela ngalokundlulele futsi bahlala balungele kusita".
tgt: re na le baritibatsamaikutlo ba ba siameng ba ba nang le tlhokomelo e bile ba nna ba le gone ka metlha go thusa," o rialo.

src: ungalibika njani licala lekudlwengulwa emaphoyiseni: ■ kwekucala, yani emtfolamphilo uyohlolwa.
tgt: o bega jang kgetse ya petelelo kwa sepodising: ■ sa ntlha, o ya kwa tliliniking go tlhatlhobiwa.

src: lombiko utawuba yincenye yelifayela lalelicala kantsi kutawusita emaphoyisa kutsi abambe lona lotsintsekako.
tgt: pegelo e tla nna karolo ya kgetse mme e tla thusa sepodisi go tshwara motlolamolao.

src: ■ hamba uye emaphoyiseni lasedvute nawe uyovula licala.
tgt: ■ morago o ye kwa seteišeneng se se gaufi sa sepodisi go bula kgetse.

src: leliphoyisa litakubuta imininingwane yakho nekutsi kwentekeni kuwe.
tgt: lepodisi le tla go botsa dipotso tse di ka ga wena le go go botsa ka se se go diragaletseng.

src: phendvula ubatjele liciniso uzame nekukhumbula yonkhe imininingwane ngendlela longakhona ngayo.
tgt: araba ka dikarabo ka boammaruri mme o leke go gakologelwa dintlha tse di ntsinyana ka fa o ka kgonang.

src: kungahle kube yinchubo lebuhlungu, kodvwa lolwatiso lutawusita nakwentiwa luphenyo.
tgt: e ka nna tiragalo e e botlhoko, fela tshedimosetso e tla thusa sepodisi mo dipatlisisong ■ kopa dinomoro tsa mogala tsa lepodisi le le batlisisang kgetse, gore o kgone go letsa go itse se se diragalang ka kgetse.

src: kubhalisela kuvota kutakwentiwa ngendlovulenkhulu 2018 more matshediso iiec imemetele imphela sontfo yekucala yeku bhalisela kuvota kwe mnyaka we2019 futsi ice la labo labafanelekile eveni lonkhe kutsi bavakashele titeshi tabo tekuvota bayo buyeketa imininingwane yabo eluhlwini lwekuvota noma babhalisele kuvota.
tgt: mopitlwe 2018 kgatiso 1go ikwadisetsa ditlhopho go tla simolola ka mopitlwe 2018. more matshediso iec ya aforika borwa e goeleditse mafelo a beke a ntlha a go ikwadisetsa ditlhopho tsa 2019 mme e ro tloeditse batlhophi ba ba du meletsweng go ralala naga go etela diteišene tsa bona tsa go tlhophela go tlhabolola dintlha tsa bona mo lenaaneng la ba tlhophi kgotsa go ikwadise tsa ditlhopho.

src: umphatsi lomkhulu wekuvotisa walekhomishini sy mamabolo utsite tonkhe titeshi tekuvotisa leti22 612 titawuvulwa kumphelaso ntfo yamhla ti10 kuya mhla ti11 indlovu 2018, kusuka nge nsimbi ye8 ekuseni kuyo shaya insimbi ye5 entsa mbama kute kube lula futsi kuhambisane netidzingo tebavoti tekubuyeketa imini ningwane yabo noma teku bhalisa.
tgt: motlhankedimogolo wa ditlhopho sy mamabolo o rile diteišene tsotlhe tsa go tlhophela di le 22612 di tla bulwa mo mafelong a beke a di 10 le di 11 tsa mopitlwe 2018 go tloga ka ura ya bo robedi mo mosong go fitlha ka ura ya botlhano maitsiboa, go dira dilo bonolo le go siamela gore batlhophi ba tlha bolole dintlha tsa bona tsa i kwadiso kgotsa ba ikwadise.

src: uma ngabe utfutsele endzaweni lensha kusukela wagcina kubhalisela kuvota, kufuneka uphindze ubhalise esigodzini sakho sekuvota lesisha.
tgt: fa ele gore o fudugetse kwa lefelong le le ntšhwa e sale ikwadiso ya gago ya go tlhopha e e fetileng, o tshwanetse go ya go ikwadisa gape mo kgaolong e ntšhwa ya go tlho phela.

src: takhamuti taseningizimu afrika letineminyaka leli16 nangetulu futsi letina matisi losemtsetfweni noma simathikhadi tingabhalisela kuvota.
tgt: baagi ba aforika borwa ba ba dingwaga di le 16 kgotsa go feta mme ba na le lekwa loitshupo kgotsa karataitshu po tsa semmuso ba ka ikwa disetsa go tlhopha.

src: uma ungakabhalisi, angeke uvunyelwe kuvota ngemnyaka we2019.
tgt: fa o sa ikwa disa, o ka se letlelelwe go tlho pha ka 2019. batlhophi ba ba ikwadisi tseng bao dintlha tsa bona tsa bonno di sa tlhageleleng mo lenaaneng la batlhophi, ba ka tlamela ka tshedimosetso e e tlhokegang kwa diteišeneng tsa bona tsa go tlhopha ka nako ya go ikwa disa.

src: "sifuna bavoti bete basebentise lelitfuba," kwasho mamabolo.
tgt: "re tlhoka gore batlhophi ba tlhagelele mme ba dirise tšhono e" go bua mamabolo.

src: "ikhomishini yelukhetfo nanyalo ayinawo emakheli ebavoti laba2.8 yetigidzi.
tgt: "khomišene ya ditlhopho e santse e tlhaela diaterese tse di ka nnang dimilione di le 2.8 tsa batlhophi.

src: sinalamanye emakheli la3.5 yetigidzi latsatfwa ‘nje ngalangakapheleli’.
tgt: re na le gape le dimilione di le 35 tsa diaterese tseo e leng gore di kaiwa di sa felela kgotsa di tlhagelela ga ntsi ka nako e le ngwe.

src: loluhlobo lwemakheli ludzinga kucutju ngulwa nekucinisekiswa kutsi ingabe kukhona yini leminye imininingwane le khona", kwangeta mamabolo.
tgt: karolo eno e tlhoka tshetshereganyo go netefatsa gore a mme go na le dintlha tse dingwe tse di leng teng" a tlaleletsa.

src: ikhomishini itfole ema kheli ngekusebentisa tindlela letehlukene, letifaka kubuye ketwa kwemarekhodi, ema fayela kanye nemaakhayivu kubuka nekubhala emakheli laniketwe bavoti kuleminyaka le20 leyengcile; kugco gcwe emakheli kulolukhetfo lwabomasipala lwemnyaka we2016; nekungena umuti ngemuti ngembi kwetimphe lasontfo tekubhalisela ku votela lukhetfo lwekuvala tikhewu.
tgt: khomišene e dirile dipa tlisiso ka ga diaterese tse, e di risa ditsela tse di farologaneng go akaretsa tekolo ya direkoto, difaele le diakhaefe go netefatsa le go boloka diaterese tseo ba tlhophi ba tlametseng ka tso na mo dingwageng di le 20 tse di fetileng; go kgoboka nya diaterese ka nako ya di tlhopho tsa bo mmasepala tsa 2016; le go tsena ntlo le ntlo pele ga mafelo a beke ya ikwadiso tebang le go tsweletsa ditlhophotlalele tso.

src: uma kudzingeka, bavoti labatfolwa babhalise etigodzini tekuvota letingakafaneli, basuswa, njengoba kubekiwe kusigaba 12 (1)(d) semtsetfo welukhetfo.

src: "sitfole futsi sasebentisa, lapho kunekwenteka khona, idatha yemakheli lebuya kuleminye imitfombo yembu so lefana netelubalobalo taseningizimu afrika, ieje nsi yekuvikeleka kwete nhlalo yaseningizimu afrika, itelkom, temaposi aseni ngizimu afrika kanye naku litiko lasekhaya", kwasho mamabolo.

src: londvolota bobhejane bakitsi more matshediso indvuna yetemvelo, edna molewa, utfule umbiko walokuchubekako wekucala wemnya ka we2018 lomayelana ne ndlelamasu yahulumende yekubambisana ekulweni nekutingelwa kwabobhejane.
tgt: boloka ditshukudu tsa rona more matshediso tona ya merero ya tikologo, edna mole wa o rebotse pegelo ya ntlha ya kgatelopele ya 2018 ka ga tsamaiso ya puso ya togamaano e e tswaragane tsweng ya go lwantsha go tsomiwa ga ditshukudu.

src: lombiko, lobuye ufake ikota yekugcina yemnyaka we2017, ukhomba imphumelelo kulinani lekubopha, kuphenya kanye nekugwe tjwa kwalabo labatingela ngalokungekho emtsetfweni nalabashushumbisa bo bhejane kanye nekuncipha lokuncane kwabobhejane labatingelwe ngalokungekho emtsetfweni eveni lonkhe ngemnyaka we2017 (1028), uma kucatsaniswa nemnyaka we2016 (1054).
tgt: pegelo, eo gape e akaretsang kotara ya bofelo ya ngwaga wa 2017, e bontsha kgatelopele mo palong ya ditlhatlhelo, dipatlisiso le katlego ya go bonwa molato ga batsomi ba ditshukudu le batlodisathoto ka bokhukhuntshwane le kwelotlase e nnye ya palo ya ditshukudu tse di tsomilweng naga ka bophara ka ngwaga wa 2017(1028), fa go bapa ntshwa le ngwaga wa 2016(1054).

src: ngemnyaka we2017 kubanjwe emahlandla lasiphohlongo bashushumbi si betimphondvo tabhejane esikhumuleweni setindiza semave ngemave ior tambo, kwaboshwa basolwa labatingela ngalokungekho emtsetfweni bobhejane laba502, basolwa labatsengisa bobhejane laba16, lokwenta lenombolo ifike ku518, le khomba kuncipha kusuka ku608 ngemnyaka we2016.
tgt: ka ngwaga wa 2017 go nnile le diphamolo di le 8 tsa dina ka tsa ditshukudu kwa boe mafofane ba or tambo mme go tlhatlhetswe babelaelwa ba batsomi ba ditshukudu ba le 502 le babelaelwa ba bagwebi ka dinaka tsa ditshukudu ba le 16, seno se tlisa palo go 518, kwelotlase go tswa go 680 ya ngwaga wa 2016.

src: "lokudzabukisako ku tsi, kuboshwe tisebenti tetfu leti21 tiboshelwa emacala lahambisana nekutingelwa lokungekho emtsetfweni kwabobhejane ngemnyaka we2017", kwasho indvuna molewa.
tgt: "ka maswabi batlhankedi ba le 21 go tswa mo badiring ba rona ba tlhatlhetswe mabapi le ditiro tse di amanang le go tsomiwa ga ditshukudu ka 2017" go bua tona edna molewa.

src: kucedza kutingela lokungekho emtsetfweni hulumende nebalingani bakhe basungule tindlela letehlukahlukene tekucedza kutingelwa lokungakavumeleki kwabobhejane, letifaka tinhlelo tekugadza nekuntji ngela emapaki avelonkhe kanye nekusebentisa ithe khnoloji yekugucula simo.
tgt: se, se ama jang moruo wa nagapuso le badirisanammogo le yona e tsentse tirisong ditse la tse di farologaneng tsa go fokotsa go tsomiwa ga ditshu kudu go akaretsa manaane a go tlhola gangwe le gape ga ditsha tsa diphologolo tsa bosetšhaba ka tiriso ya theke noloji ya maemo a a kwa go dimo.

src: emkhatsini kwabimbi dvwane nengongoni 2017, kwatingelwa ngalukunge kho emtsetfweni bobhejane laba504 ekruger national park (eknp), lokwehle nge maphesenti langema24 kunalangema662 ngemnyaka we2016.
tgt: magareng ga ferikgong le sedimonthole 2017, go tsomilwe ditshukudu di le 507 kwa setsheng sa diphologolo tse di tlhaga sa kruger national park, palo eo e leng kwa tlase ka diperesente di le 24 go na le 662 ka ngwaga wa 2016.

src: "ngenca yemiphumela yetindlelamasu tetfu tekulwa nekutingela lokungekho e mtsetfweni eknp sibona kwehla kwelinani letintfo letimayelana nekutingela lokungekho emtsetfweni kulepaki, lelikhomba kutsi beliku2662 ngemnyaka we2017 uma licatsaniswa ne2883 ngemnyaka we2016.
tgt: "ka ntlha ya togamaano ya rona ya go lwantsha go tsomiwa ga ditshukudu kwa knp re bona kwelotlase ya go tsoma ditshukudu mo ditsheng tsa diphologolo tse di tlhaga, ka 2662 e e rekotilweng ka 2017 fa go bapantshiwa le 2883 ka 2016. seno se bontsha kwelotlase ya diperesente di le 7.6" go tlhomamisa tona.

src: loku kusho kuncipha nge maphesenti la7.6," kwa cinisekisa indvuna yelitiko.
tgt: le fa gontse jalo, palo ya ditshukudu tse di tsomilweng kwa ditsheng tsa diphologolo tse di tlhaga tsa kwa kwazulu natal, kapa bokone, mpu malanga,foreisetata le bokone bophirima e ile kwa godimo.

src: kodvwake, likhulile linani labobhejane labatingelwe ngalokungekho emtsetfweni kwazulunatal, enyakatfo kapa, empumalanga, efree state kanye nasenyakatfo nshonalanga.
tgt: se, se ama jang moruo wa nagago tsomiwa ga ditshukudu le go gweba ka diphologolo tsa kwa nageng go ama kgolo ya ikonomi ya naga le go tlhamiwa ga ditiro, go akaretsa kgolo ya ikonomi e e farologaneng ya tikologo eo e tsenyeletsang ya lephata la bonajanala ka tsela e e sa siamang.

src: liculo lesive, umjeka, imiklomelo yesive, siphandla sesive netimpawu tibungata kwehlukahlukana vukuzenzele unnamed kulenyanga kunelilanga lelibekelwe kubungata kucala kwenkululeko nentsandvo yelinyenti kanye netimphumelelo tabo bonkhe ba ntfu baseningizimu afrika le ticedza kutondzana, kungevani kanye netemlandvo lobuhlu ngu netekwakha likusasa lelifa nanako ngekubambisana.

src: vuk’uzenzele ibuka kubaluleka kwalolusuku nekutsi lisho kutsi ni kitsi sibantfu baseningizimu afrika.

src: mhla ti27 kumabasa 1994 ini ngizimu afrika yabamba lukhe tfo lwayo lwekucala lwentsandvo yelinyenti.

tgt: ka la 27 moranang 1994 aforika borwa e nnile le ditlho pho tsa ntlha tsa temokerasi tse di sa kgethololeng ka bo morafe.

src: loku miklomelo lesezingeni lelisetulu kakhulu leniketwa ngulelive, ngumengameli, aniketa takhamuti talelive nebantfu bemave angaphandle labahlonishwa kakhulu.
tgt: puso e ntšhwa e ne ya tlhophiwa ka fa tlase ga boe teledipele jwa moporesidente yo o hulereng nelson mandela.

src: umtsetfosisekelo waseningizimu afrikaumtsetfosisekelo wabhalwa ngekulandzela sigaba 5 semtsetfo sisekelo wesikhashana (umtsetfo 200 wemnyaka we1993) lowacala kuvunywa mkhandlu wemtsetfosisekelo mhla ti8 inkhwekhweti 1996. wasayinwa waba ngumtsetfo mhla ti10 ingongoni 1996. timpawu tetfu tesive iningizimu afrika yehlukile ku lamanye emave ngenca yekutsi singabungata kuhlukahlukana kwetfu ngekusebentisa timpawu tesive kanye nemjeka sesive, liculo lesive saseningizimu afrika kanye nesiphandla sesive.
tgt: go setse go fitlheletswe go le gontsi mo dingwageng tse dintsi, fela go sa le go ntsi go go sa ntseng go tlhokwa go dirwa go tokafatsa naga ya rona le go fetola matshelo a maaforika borwa otlhe.

src: wadvwetjwa ngilowo bekasisebenti sekusungulwa kwetiphandla tesive, isouth a frican state herald, fred brownell, wacala kusetjentiswa mhla ti27 mabasa 1994. lemibala yalomjeka ayisho lutfo ngakoke akukho kumelelwa kwetintfo tsite temhlaba leticondzaniswa nalemibala yalomjeka.
tgt: moranang ga se kgwedi fela ya go leba kwa morago go bona kwa naga e tswang gone, mme ke nako eo aforika bo rwa e ketekang bagale ba yona ba borre le ba bomme ka go dirisa dikabo tsa bosetšhaba.

src: loluphawu lwa‘v’ kulomjeka lumelele kuhlangana kwetintfo letiningi teningizimu afrika nekubamba ngekubumbana indlela leya embili.
tgt: ke diabo tsa maemo a a kwa go dimo tseo naga, ka mopore sidente wa yona, e di abelang baagi ba yona le baditšhaba ba ba botlhokwa.

src: kuphakamisa umjeka uma lomjeka ubekwe ngaloku vundlile ebondzeni, umbala lobovu kufanele ube sesincele saloyo lobukako bese kutsi lapho ucunyekwa khona kube ngenhla.
tgt: molaotheo wa aforika borwa molaotheo o ne wa kwalwa go ya ka melawana ya kgaolo 5 ya molaotheo wa nakwana (molao 200 wa 1993) mme wa amogelwa lwa ntlha ke kokoano ya molaotheo ka la 8 motsheganong 1996. wa saenwa go nna molao ka la 10 sedimonthole 1996. matshwao a rona a bosetšhaba aforika borwa ke naga e e kge thegileng ka ntlha ya fa re kgona go keteka pharologano ya rona ka go dirisa matshwao a bosetšhaba le folaga ya bosetšhaba, pina ya bosetšhaba ya aforika borwa le letshwao la setšhaba.

src: uma ubekwe wema wabuka etulu, loko locunyekwa ngako kufanele kube sesandleni sesincele saloyo lobukako bese kutsi umbala lobovu ube setulu.
tgt: moakanyetso wa yona o dirilwe ke mokwadisi wa matshwao a setšhaba wa maloba wa aforika borwa, fred brownell, mme ya dirisiwa lwa ntlha ka la 27 moranang 1994. mebala ya folaga ga e na bokao jo bo rileng mme ga go le tshwao lepe le le tshwanetseng go tsamaisiwa le mebala ya folaga.

src: uma umjeka ubekwe eceleni noma emuva kwalokhulumako, kufanele ubekwe ecaleni lesekudla laloyo lokhulumako.
tgt: ‘v’ e e mo folageng e kaya tshwaragano ya dielemente tse di farologaneng tsa aforika bo rwa le go tsamaya mmogo re le seoposengwe mo tseleng e e re lebisang kwa bokamosong.

src: uma ubekwe kulenye indzawo lapho kunemhlangano khona, kufanele ube ngasesandleni sekudla salabo labahleli phansi labalalelako.
tgt: go phaphasela ga folaga fa fologa e beilwe e tsepame mo leboteng , mmala o mohibidu o tshwanetse go nna ka fa molemeng wa motho yo o e lebileng mme setsholetsi kgotsa momeno o o tsenyang mogala o le kwa godimo.

src: siphandla sesive siphandla sesive, lephindze satiwe ngekutsi liphawu lesive, siluphawu lolukhulu lolugcamile lwesive.
tgt: mme fa e rapame, se tsholetsi sa yona se tshwane tse go nna ka fa molemeng wa motho yo o e lebileng mme mmala o mohibidu o nna kwa godimo.

src: siphandla sesive siyincenye lenkhulu yesingcivito sesive.
tgt: letshwao la setšhaba letshwao la setšhaba, le le itse geng jaaka emboleme ya puso, ke letshwao le le kwa godimo le le bonalang la naga.

src: idokhumenti lenesingcivito se sive ibaluleke kakhulu ikhomba emandla ekuphatsa lamakhulu, loku kuchaza kutsi ivunywe ngumengameli weningizimu afrika.
tgt: letshwao la setšhaba ke karolo e e botlhokwa ya kano e kgolo.

src: siphandla sesive saseningizi mu afrika sasungulwa ngelusu ku lwenkhululeko ngemnyaka we2000.
tgt: setlankana se se bontshang kgatiso ya kano e kgolo mo go sona se bontsha thata e e feletseng ka se kaya fa se atlanegisitswe ke moporesidente wa aforika borwa.

src: tintfo letikuso tihlelwe ngendlela lekhombisa kusimama nekubaluleka lokukhulu.
tgt: letshwao la setšhaba le tha nkgolotswe ka letsatsi la kgolo losego ka 2000. dielemente tse di mo go lona di beilwe ka tsela e e supang tlhomamo le botlhokwa.

src: kulwa nesomiso lesikhulu vukuzenzele unnamed njengaloku somiso sesifinyelele emazingeni lapho se kunenkinga lenkhulu enya katfo kapa nasemphuma langa kapa, lapho emazinga emanti emadamu kumasipa la welidolobhakati wasenel son mandela bay asangem aphesenti lange25 kuphela, sesikhatsi nyalo sekutsi bantfu baseningizimu afrika ba bumbane bonge lamanti layi mvelakancane nalaligugu.
tgt: go lwantsha komelelo e e kgologadi vukuzenzele unnamed jaaka komelelo e setse e fitlhile mo maemong a a diphatsa kwa kapa bokone le kwa kapa botlhaba, moo me tsi a a leng kwa matamong a masepala wa teropo kgolo ya nelson mandela bay a emeng mo maemong a 25%, ke nako ya gore maaforika borwa a tshwaragane go bo loka motswedi ono o o seng montsi e bile o le botlhokwa.

src: somiso sikhatsi lesidze sekuna kwemvula lencane kakhulu lokuholela ekutseni kuswelakale emanti.
tgt: komelelo ke paka e e telele ya go tlhoka pula e leng se se tlholang metsi a a tlhaelang.

src: ngekusho kwadkt.
tgt: go ya ka ngaka mathieu roualt, moporofesara yo mogo lwane kwa yunibesiting ya kapa mo lefapheng la dithuto tsa mawatle, setlhodi se segolo sa komelelo ke seabe sa el niño mmogo le phetogo ya maemo a loapi.

src: mathieu roualt, longusolwati kulitiko letekufundza ngelwandle enyuvesi yasekapa, timbangela letinkhulu tesomiso yiel niño nekuntjintja kwesimo selitulu.
tgt: "el niño ke selo sa tlhago se se itlelang ka dipaka tse di rileng mme e iponagatsa gangwe le gape morago ga dingwaga di ka nna tharo go isa go di le tlhano mme e ka nna sebaka sa dingwa ga di ka nna pedi e sa tsamaye.

src: "iel niño sehlakalo semvelo lesenteka ngetikhatsi letitsite lesibuya njalo emva kweminya ka lemitsatfu kuya kulesihlanu futsi singahlala iminyaka lemi bili.
tgt: e oketsa maemo a mogote kwa lewatleng la pacific le la india, mme seno se ka tlhola komelelo e e seng kana ka sepe," o tlha lositse jalo.

src: lesimo senyusa emazinga ekushisa elwandle ipacific kanye nelwandle lwasendiya, loko kubese kubangela kutsi kube netimo tesomiso," kwasho yena njalo.
tgt: phetogo ya maemo a loapi e tlhalosiwa gore ke phetogo mo setlwaeding sa loaping mo le fatsheng ka bophara kgotsa mo kgaolong mme e simolotseng mo gare go fitlha kwa bokhu tlhong jwa ngwagakgolo wa bo 20 ebile e tlhotlhelediwa bogolose golo ke maemo a a tlhatlogileng a khabonotaeokosaete ya lefaufau e e tswang mo tirisong ya ditu kisi tsa fosele.

src: kugucuka kwesimo selitulu kuchazwa njengekuntjintja kwetimo telitulu mhlaba wo nkhe nome esifundzeni, lokuyi ntfo leyacala emkhatsini kwaya ngasekupheleni kwemnya kalikhulu we20 kubangwa kakhulu kwenyuka kwemazi nga esikhutsa emoyeni lesikhi citeka uma kusetjentiswa emafutsa emvelo.
tgt: "mo ngwagakgolong yo o fetileng dinaga tsa borwa jwa aforika di ntse di boga ka ntlha ya diphetogo tsa ngwaga le ngwaga mo phetogong ya loapi, e leng se se tlhodileng komelelo e e kgologadi le kgoreletsego mo di tsheding tsa kwa ma watleng le mo tikolo gong.

src: "kuleminyaka lelikhulu leye ngcile iafrika lengaseningi zimu ibukene nekugucuka kwesimo selitulu iminyaka ngeminyaka, lokuholele eso misweni lesikhulu kanye ne kutsikameteka tindlela teku hlalisana kwetintfo letiphilako taselwandle kanye netase mhlabatsini.
tgt: diphetogo tseno di ama intaseteri ya temothuo, metsi a a beetsweng motsi wa lešekere le dikgwebo tsa bodirelatlhapi mmogo le ikonomi ka kakaretso.

src: letingucuko tine mtselela lomubi etimbonini tekulima, kutilondvolotama nti nasetinhlantini kanyeke nemnotfo ngebubanti bawo.
tgt: gape di ama le kelelo ya metsi mo melatswaneng le mo ditshi ngwaneng mmogo le go šwa ga dikotla mo lewatleng," ngaka roualt o tlhalositse jalo.

src: tiphindze futsi tibe nemtselela lomubi ekugeleteni kwemanti emifuleni kanye nasetitfonjeni temvelo kanye nekungena elwa ndle kudla lokungumsoco ," kuchaza yena njalo dkt.
tgt: diphetogo tseno di utlwiwa bogolosegolo ke aforika borwa ka ntlha ya fa naga ya rona e setse e ntse e na le pula e e seng kalo e e ka lekanang dimililitara (ml) di le 450 ka ngwaga, fa e bapisi wa le eo dinaga tse dingwe ka bophara di itemogelang yona e e leng kanaka 860ml.

src: yini imitselela lemibi yesomiso?
tgt: ditlamorago tsa komelelo ke eng?

src: ngendlovulencane, litiko letekubusa ngekuhla nganyela netendzabuko (icogta) basihlela kabusha batsi lesomiso asisasiyo inhlekelele yesifundza kuphela kepha seyinhlekelele yavelonkhe.
tgt: ka tlhakole, lefapha la puso tshwaraganelo le merero ya setso (cogta) le tlositse komelelo mo maemong ao e neng e beilwe mo go ona a matlhotlhapelo a porofense mme la a baya mo maemong a bosetšhaba.

src: "ngemuva kwekuhlola futsi bukhulu nemtse lela lomubi kakhulu walesomiso lesichu bekako, lesesichu bekele kulokungenani etifundzeni letintsatfu, labalawula tinhlekele le baphindze futsi basihlela kabusha lesomiso batsi sesiyi nhlekelele yavelonkhe nyalo," kwasho inhloko yesikhungo savelonkhe lesilawula tinhle kelele, dkt.
tgt: "morago ga go lekolasešwa bogolo le bogale jwa komelelo e e tsweletseng ga jaana mo diporofenseng di ka nna tharo, botsamaisi jwa ditiragalo tsa matlhotlhapelo bo ne jwa sutisa le go baya sešwa komelelo go nna matlhotlhapelo a bosetšha ba," ga rialo tlhogo ya tikwati kwe ya ditirelo tsa botsamaisi jwa ditiragalo tsa matlhotlhape lo, ngaka mmaphaka tau.

src: nanome nje kulukhuni kukala imitselela lemibi yalesomiso emnotfweni, kodvwa kube nemtselela lomkhulu lomubi emkhakheni kwetekulima.
tgt: le fa ditlamorago tsa ikonomi tse di bakiwang ke komelelo go le bokete go ka di nopola, go nnile le ditlamorago tse di boitshegang mo lekaleng la temothuo.

src: enshonalanga kapa, loku sifundza sesibili lesikhicita kakhulu kutekulima talelive, kwaphela imisebenti lelinga niselwa kule21 000 ekoteni ye sitsatfu kulomnyaka lophelile.
tgt: kwa kapa bophirima, e leng porofense ya bobedi mo nageng mo go tsenyeng letsogo mo seelong sotlhe sa ditlhagisiwa tsa naga mo ngwageng (gdp) sa temothuo, go nnile le ditiro di ka nna 21 000 tse di latlhegileng ngogola mo kotareng ya boraro.

src: kukhicitwa kwakolo kwehla ngemaphesenti lange47 nga2017 loko kungabanga kushoda kwemalitha latigidzi letinge90 eliwayini langatsengiselwa emave angephandle kumbe khona lapha eveni.
tgt: tlhagiso ya korong e wetse kwa tlase ka 47% mo ngwageng wa 2017 mme e bile go na le kgona galo ya gore go ka tlhaelwa ka dilitara di ka nna dimilione di le 90 tsa beine tse di rekisediwang dinaga tsa kwa ntle le tsa ka fa nageng.

src: kweswelakala kwemanti kutawuba nemtselela lomubi ekuhanjisweni kwekungcola ngemanti, ekunakekeleni te mphilo kanye netekuvakasha.
tgt: go tlhaela ga metsi gape go tla nna le seabe se se sa itumediseng mo kgelelolesweng, tlhokome long ya boitekanelo le mo boja naleng.

src: yini lokwentiwako kute kubukanwe nalesimo?

src: iapp yetigitjelwa temmango tasegauteng vukuzenzele unnamed litiko lasegauteng le temigwaco nekutfutsa letfule iapp yamakhe lekhikhini, leyatiwa ngekut si pheceleti yigauteng on the move, kute luhlelo lwetitfutsi temmango lwente kutsi bagibeli bachumane netindlela tekutfu tsa letahlukahlukene ngapha ndle kwenkinga.
tgt: gauteng e nolofatsa tiriso ya dipalangwa tsa botlhe vukuzenzele unnamed lefapha la ditsela le dipalangwa la gauteng le thankgolo tse app ya megala ya ka fa potleng, gauteng on the move, tebang le thulaga nyo ya yona ya dipalangwa tsa botlhe e e kgontshang bapala mi go golagana le dipalangwa tse di farologaneng bonolo.

src: igauteng on the move itawususa kungabata loku khona nawusebentisa titfutsi temmango, ngobe inika bagibeli lwatiso mbamba lwesikhatsi, ishejuli yesigitjelwa kanye neti ndleko tekuhamba ngegautrain‚ metrobus‚ a re yeng‚ rea vaya‚ metrorail‚ ngegautrain bus ser vices‚ johannesburg city sight seeing bus‚ tshwane bus services kanye netinsita tematekisi.
tgt: gauteng on the move e tla fe disa ketsaetsego ya go dirisa dipalangwa tsa botlhe, ka ntlha ya fa e tla bo e tlamela bapalami ka tshedimosetso e e leng mo dinakong, lenaane la dipalangwa le dituelelo tsa gautrain‚ metrobus‚ a re yeng‚ rea vaya‚ metrorail‚ gautrain bus services‚ johannesburg city sightseeing bus‚ tshwane bus services mmogo le tsa ditirelo tsa dithekesi.

src: akhuluma ngesikhatsi kwe tfulwa leapp ehhovisi lalabo labayisungulile lelisemidrand esikhatsini lesisandza kwendlu la, indvuna yetekutfutsa ye sifundza sasegauteng ismail vadi utsite litiko lisibonile vele sidzingo sekutsi kube khona tebuchwepheshe letihlakaniphile kanye neluhlelo lwetekutfutsa loluhlakaniphile njengalokufaka ligalelo ekutfutfukisweni kwete kutfutsa.
tgt: fa a ne a bua kwa thankgo lolong ya app eno kwa dika ntorong tsa batlhagisi ba app eno kwa midrand mo malobeng, mokhuduthamaga wa dipalangwa tsa gauteng ismail vadi o rile lefapha le bone botlhokwa jwa thekenoloji le thulaganyo e e tlhalefileng ya dipalangwa jaaka seabe sa go tokafatsa thulaganyo ya dipalangwa.

src: "hulumende wesifundza sasegauteng wente lutjalotimali lwesikhatsi sakhe, lwemitamo kanye nemitfombolusito ekwakh iweni kwalesihleliluhambo kute kutsi kubelula kutsi bagibeli bakhone kuchumana lula netinhlobo tetitfutsi letinkhulu talesifundza.
tgt: "puso ya porofense ya gauteng e beeleditse nako, matsapa a yona le didirisiwa go tokafatsa leeto leno la togomaano le le kgontsha ng banamedi go golagana bonolo le dipalangwa tse dingwe tse dikgolo mo porofenseng.

src: "sesivele siyawabona emandla etebuchwepheshe bekucamba lokusha lahlela kabusha tigi tjelwa temmango.
tgt: "re setse re simolotse go itemogela maatla a boitshi mololedi jwa thekenoloji moo bo rulaganyang sešwa ditirelo tsa dipalangwa tsa botlhe.

src: kute kunga bata kutsi tingucuko tebuchwe pheshe emhlabeni wonkhe ticala tingucuko letinkhulu emkhakheni wetekutfutsa te mmango, natsi kufanele kutsi sitemukele futsi sititayele leti ngucuko," kwasho yena njalo.
tgt: ga re na pelaelo ya gore diphetogo tsa thekenoloji mo lefatsheng di setse di simolotse go tlisa diphetogo mo lekaleng la dipalangwa, mme re tshwanetse go rwala morwalo wa rona re gatele pele ka diphetogo tseno," o buile jalo.

src: vadi ucinisekise kutsi sifundza sitawuchubeka ngekusebentisa umcondvo lomusha, lucwaningo kanye nentfutfuko kugcugcutela kutsi kube nesifundza lesenta tintfo ngekuhlakanipha kute kube nemphumelelo nekufinyelela ti nsita tetigitjelwa.
tgt: vadi o totobaditse gore porofense e tla tswelela pele go dirisa boitshimololedi, boba tlisisi le tlhabololo go tsholetsa porofense e e dirisang thekenolo ji go tokafatsa tolamo le phitlhelesego ya ditirelo tsa dipalangwa.

src: nasebayidvonsile kuin thanethi, leapp itawusita labo labayisebentisako kutsi bahlele luhambo lwabo ngekutsi bakhe tse indlela yekuhamba laba yifunako, sikhatsi sekuhamba kanye nalokunye labangakhetsa kuko, njengeluhambo lolufisha nalolushiphe kakhuluumfundzi wasejohannesburg nalomunye webagibeli glen dlamini batsi leapp itakwenta tinkhulungwane tebagibeli kutsi bangasakhatsateki nabafuna kuhamba.
tgt: gang fa e setse e tsentswe mo mogaleng wa ka fa potleng, app eno e kgontsha badirisi go rulaga nya maeto a bona ka go tlhopha senamelwa se ba se batlang, dinako tse ba tla tsayang maeto ka tsone le tse dingwe, tse di jaaka maeto a makhutshwane le a a seng tlhwatlhwa godimo.

src: "impela lena yiapp lemanga lisako sibili.
tgt: moithuti wa kwa yunibesiti ya johannesburg yo gape e leng monamedi glen dlamini a re app eno e tla theosa matshwafo a bapalami ba le diketekete.

src: lusha luyalwemukela luhlelo lweyes vukuzenzele unnamed masego temane uyatfokota ku tsi atfole lwati lwemsebenti, lolutawuha mbisana neticu takhe tedi ploma yehuman resource management, njengalongene lele kuletinsita tekucashwa kwelusha (iyes).
tgt: bašwa ba re yes ka ga diphatlhatiro vukuzenzele unnamed masego temane o itumeletse go kokoanya mai temogelo a tiro, a a tsamaela nang le tipoloma ya gagwe ya human resource ma nagement , jaaka e le karolo ya ditirelo tsa go thapiwa ga bašwa (yes).

src: yes, lesandza kuvulwa ngu mengameli cyril ramapho sa, ihlose kulungiselela lusha kutsi batfole umsebenti iba nikete emakhono ebuchwe pheshe ladzingekako kute kuciniswe ku tfutfukiswa kwemno tfo.
tgt: yes, e mo malobeng e thankgolotsweng ke moporesitente cyril rama phosa, maitlhomo a yona ke go baakanyetsa bašwa diti ro le go ba tlamela ka bo kgoni jwa setegeniki jo bo tlhokegang go ka lopana le ikonomi e e itshetlegileng ka diintaseteri.

src: temane uyachaza kweku tsi ngemuva kwekutfola ticu nga2016 akazange akhone kufaka ticelo temsebenti ngoba bekangenalo lwati lwemsebenti loludzingeka ko.
tgt: temane o tlhalosa gore morago ga go aloga ka 2016 o ne a retelelwa ke go dira dikopo tsa ditiro ka ntlha ya fa a ne a sena maitemogelo a a matshwanedi.

src: "bekulukhuni kufuna umse benti ngaphandle kwekuba nelwati lwemsebenti.
tgt: "go ne go le bokete e le ruri go batlana le tiro ntle le maitemogelo.

src: nge nhlahla ngahlangabetana ne lulaway recruitment age ncy lesebentisana neyes, kantsi banginiketa litfuba lokufundzela umsebenti e msebentini, iinternship.
tgt: ka lesego ke ne ka kopana le ba lu laway recruitment agency ba ba dirisanang le ba yes mme ba ne ba nnaya tšhono ya borutelatiro.

src: "iyes ingumtamo loyinhla nganisela wahulumende, ti nhlangano tetisebenti nema bhizinisi kutsi banikete ba ntu labasha baseningizimu afrika labasigidzi misebenti lekhokhelwayo kuleminyaka lemitsatfu letako.

src: mengameli cyril rama phosa wente lesimeme telo ngalesikhatsi semci mbi wekubeka indlovukati yebalobedu emokwakwa ila stadium ebolobedu, gamodjadji elimpopo.

src: umsebenti weningizimu afrika kufundzisa lusha more matshediso indvuna yetemfundvo lephakeme nekucece sha nalendi pandor utsi iningizimu afrika iyakhona kunika umfundzate bantfwa na bemindeni lephuyile na lehola imiholo lemincane labangena emanyuvesi nasemakolishi emfundvo nekuceceshela umsebenti wemakhono (ematvet) nga2018.
tgt: aforika borwa e na le maikarabelo a go tsenya bašwa sekolo more matshediso tona ya lefapha la thu to e kgolwane le kati so naledi pandor a re aforika borwa e na le bokgoni jwa go tlamela ka dibasari bana ba ba tswang mo malapeng a a humanegileng le ba ba tswang mo malapeng ao a iponelang letseno le le kwa tlase go bona thuto mo diyunibesiting le mo dikholejeng tsa thuto le kati so ya tiro ya matsogo le ya setegeniki (tvet) ka 2018. tona pandor o rile ke maikara belo a naga go tshegetsa bahuma negi mmogo le malapa ao a leng mo tlalelong go gaisa.

src: indvuna pandor utsite ngu msebenti walelive kwesekela leyo mindeni lephuyile.
tgt: o buile seno mo kopanong ya bobegakgang mo a neng a rebo la lenane la tsamaiso ya thuto e kgolwane e e sa duelelweng mo aforika borwa.

src: bekakhuluma nebetindzaba lapho avete khona inchubo yekucala kunikwa kwemfu ndvo yamahhala lapha eningi zimu afrika.
tgt: tona pandor o tsibositse se mmuso gore puso e beeleditse madi a mangwe gape a le kana ka r7.166 bilione go tlamela ka dibasari go bana ba ba tswang mo malapeng a a humanegileng le ba ba tswang mo malapeng ao a amogelang letseno le le kwa tlase go ya diyunibesiting le dikhole jeng tsa tvet monongwaga.

src: indvuna pandor umemetele ngalokusemtsetfweni kutsi hulumende wengete nge lutjalotimali lwetigidzigidzi letir7.166 esikhwameni semifundzate yebantfwana bemindeni lephuyile nalehola imiholo lemincane labangena emanyuvesi nasematvet kulomnyaka.
tgt: tona pandor o tlhomamisitse gore go beetswe kwa thoko r4.581 bilione go isa sekolong baithuti ba ba falotseng go ya diyunibesiti mme r2.585 bilione e beetswe baithuti ba ba yang dikholejeng tsa tvet.

src: indvuna pandor ucinisekise kutsi tigidzigidzi ler4.581 ti bekelwe eceleni labo bafundzi labafanele kungena enyuvesi netigidzi ler2.585 tibeke lwe bafundzi basemakolishi etvet.
tgt: ka ngwaga wa 2017 puso e begile gore thuto e kgolwane e tla nna mahala go baithuti ba ba dikobo dikhutshwane le ba ba tswang mo malapeng a a amo gelang letseno le le kwa tlase ga r350 000 ka ngwaga.

src: nga2017 hulumende umemetele kutsi imfundvo lephakeme itawubamahhala kubafundzi labaphuyile kanye nalabo labavela emindenini lehola ngemnyaka umholo lohlanganisiwe losengaka dvonswa letinye timali loyima lingena ler350 000. labafundzi basekelwa ngesikimu semfundzate lese ngetiwe, lesitsatsa sikhundla semalimboleko yaphambilini kanye nesikimu lesingasiwo umfundzate lophelele lesi niketwa sikimu savelonkhe sekusita bafundzi ngetimali (insfas).
tgt: baithuti ba tla tshegediwa go tswa mo sekemeng se se atolosi tsweng sa dibasari, seo se tsenang mo legatong la sekema sa mo malobeng sa kadimo le bontlha bongwe jwa dibasari seo se neng se neelwa ke sekema sa bosetšha ba sa thuso ya ditšhelete tsa thuto mo baithuting (nsfas).

src: "luphakelo lwekucala lwensfas lwekusekela bafundzi labaphuyile base manyuvesi nasemakolishi etvet lutakwenyuka kusuke la etigidzigidzini ler9.849 nga2017/18 luye etigidzigidzini letinger35.321 nga2020/21.
tgt: "motheo wa madi a a abelwang nsfas go tshegetsa baithuti ba diyunibesiti le dikholeje tsa tvet ba ba humanegileng le bao ba tswang mo malapeng a a amogelang letseno le le kwa tlase a tla okediwa go tloga go r9.849 bilione ka ngwaga wa 2017/18 go ya go r35.321 bilione ka ngwaga wa 2020/21.

src: "loku kusho kutsi kune sidzingo sekutfutfukisa tinhle lo tekusebenta ngemphumelelo kunsfas.
tgt: seno se tlhalosa tlhokego ya thulaganyo e e tokafaditsweng e bile e dira sentle mo tsamaisong ya nsfas.

src: ngaleyo ndlelake sente luphakelo lolwengetiwe lwetigidzi letir105 kulolu hlakamsebenti lwetinchitfo mali lwethemu lesekhatsi kute kusitwe insfas kutsi yandzise futsi icinise emandla ayo ekukhona kusebenta," kwasho yona njalo indvuna.
tgt: ka jalo re abelane ka madi a mangwe gape a le kana ka r105 milione mo pakeng ya letlhomeso la ditshenyegelo tsa pakagare (mtef) go thusa nsfas go oketsa le go matlafatsa mothamo wa thulaganyotsamai so ya yona," go rialo tona.

src: bafundzi labafanele, kuyo yonkhe iminyaka yekufundza kwabo, lababhalise emakolishi etvet ahulumende batawu tfola umfundzate kukhokhela imali yekufundza kanye neti nsita tekufundza.
tgt: baithuti ba ba falotseng, mo dingwageng tsotlhe tsa fa ba tla bo ba ithuta, ba ba ikwadiseditse ng makwalo a bosetšhaba (thuto ya ditiro tsa diatla) le manane a thuto mo dikholejeng mo dikho lejeng tsa botlhe tsa tvet ba tla amogela dibasari tsa go duelela dithuto le didirisiwa tsa go ithuta.

src: litiko letasekhaya limemetela kulwa nemigca lemidze more matshediso litiko letasekhaya lente lisu lekwenta ti ntfo kucinisekisa kutsi takhamuti aticitsi sikhatsi lesidze emigceni.
tgt: lefapha la merero ya selegae le lwantsha mela more matshediso lefapha la merero ya selegae le tsenya mo tirisong leanotiro la go netefatsa fa baagi ba sa senyegelwe ke nako mo me leng.

src: ngekusho kwendvuna yetasekhaya malusi gigaba imigca lemidze beyibangwa linani lelisetulu lebantfu, indzawo lengakaneli yelihhovisi lelingembili, tinkinga tebuholi kanye nekuvalwa kwemahho visi ngabomgcibelo.
tgt: go ya ka tona ya merero ya selegae malusi gigaba mela e meleele e ne e tlholwa ke thologelo e e kwa godimo ya baagi, dikantorobogorogelo tse dinnye, matsapa a boeteledipele le go tswalwa ga dikantoro ka bo lamatlhatso.

src: kulungisa lenkinga, litiko liba la linani lemahhovisi alo eveni lonkhe kutfola kutsi ngukutiphi tindzawo lapho kudzingeka kwentiwa ncono khona tinsi takalo.
tgt: go baakanya mathata a, lefapha le dirile dipatlisiso labo la tsaya tshwetso ya go bona gore ke dikantoro dife mo mafelong afe tseo go tlhokegang gore go tokafadiwe thebolotirelo mo go tsona.

src: "sitawusungula luklayo lwe kwenetiswa kwetakhamuti, sente kutsi sikhungo sekuchumana se takhamuti sisebente ngemphu melelo, kutfola sisombululo setakhamuti letingena tinga kalindzelwa kanye nendzawo yelihhovisi lelingembili, kubuka nekutsi ngeke yini kube nelu hlelo lolusha lwekusebenta emashifu, kulungisa loluhlelo langcondvomshini lolungakati nti, kwenyusa lizinga lekuvaka sha emahhovisi etfu kwemame nenja lamakhulu, kwenta ncono kuhamba kwemsebenti kanye nekwengeta lizinga lekuchu manana netakhamuti," kwasho yona njalo indvuna.
tgt: "re tla tsenya mo tirisong le naane la go tlhola kgotsofalo ya baagi, re lolamise le borakanelo jwa tlhaeletsano le go tlhomamisa gore bo dira ka tshwanelo, re bone tharabololo mabapi le baagi ba ba etelang dikantoro ba sa solofelwa le go oketsa sebaka sa dikanto robogorogelo, re tlhomamise le kgonagalo ya go tsenya mo tirisong dithulaganyo tse di ntšhwa tsa go theogela, re lebagane le dithulaganyo tse di bokoa, re goletse le diketelo tse di sa begiwang tsa batsama isibagolo mo dikantorong, re tokafatse kelelo ya tiro gape re tokafatse tsela ya tlhaeletsano le baagi," go tlhomamisa tona.

src: lamasu ekwenta tintfo atawu cala kusebenta njengetinya tselo tekungenelela tethemu lemfisha, lesemkhatsini kanye neyesikhatsi lesidze.
tgt: maanotiro ano, a tlile go tsengwa mo tirisong e le ditha rabololo tsa pakakhutshwe le tsa pakatelele.

src: indvuna ichaze kutsi leti nsayeya ngeke tisonjululwe ngekusebentisa tinyatselo tekungenelela letilungisa tintfo ngekushesha futsi icele umma ngo kutsi ubeketele ngesikhatsi litiko lisacala kutisebentisa.
tgt: tona o tlhalositse fa dikgwe tlho tseno di ka se rarabolo lwe ka tsela ya go dira o fetisa fela tiro mme o ikuetse mo setšhabeng gore se nne le bopelotelele fa lefapha le semeletse go tsenya ditharabololo tseno mo tirisong.

src: "sitimisele ngekwenta konkhe lokusemandleni etfu kulwa nemphi yekuma emigceni, nanome kunetinkinga telitiko kanye naletinye tinsayeya," kwasho indvuna gigaba.
tgt: "re ikemiseditse tota go dira bojotlhe jwa rona go khutlisa mela le fa re ntse re itemogela matsapa le dikgwetlho tsa maemo a loago", go bua tona gigaba.

src: ngembikwekumemetelwa kwemasu ekwenta tintfo litiko litsite akube khona umbiko wekuhlola kutfola kutsi lemigca singayilawula njani ncono kanye nekwenta ncono tinsitakalo talo.
tgt: pele ga kitsiso ya maanotiro ano, lefapha le ne la rebola thulaganyo ya go tlhatlhoba gore ke tsela efe e e maleba ya go tsamaisa le go laola mela le go tokafatsa ditirelo tsa yona.

src: lomkhuba waphawula nge tinhlelo tengcondvomshini letingakatinti, inchubo lete imphumelelo yekuhamba kwemsebenti kanye netindle lamasu tekuchumana letinga hambisani letiholela ekutseni kube netakhamuti letingane tiseki kanye nekuba khona kwemigca lemidze.
tgt: pego e tlhagisitse fa dithulaganyo tse di bokoa, kelelotiro e e sa lolamang le mesolatogamaano ya tlhaeletsano e e sa rulagangwang sentle e le tsona tse di tlogelang baagi ba sa kgotsofala le mela e meleele.

src: ngekusho kwendvuna, lama phuzu lalandzelako enta lenki nga kutsi ichubekiseleke embili: ■ kulawula lokungekho ezingeni kulamanye emahhovisi ■ kungasebentiseki ngemphu melelo kwetisebenti ■ kuswelakala kweluhlelo lwekucasha ■ kungalawuli ngemphumelelo imigca ■ kuchubeka ngasikhatsi sinye kweluhlelo lolwentisa bantfu kanye nalolo lolutentekelako ■ kungasatjalaliswa ngekuli ngana kwemahhovisi ngekubuka bantfu labakhona lwatiso lolungasilo lolumayelana nekutsi ema bhuku amatisi lanebhakodi angeke asabakhona.
tgt: go ya ka tona, mabaka a a latelang a okeditse mathata le go feta:■ tsamaiso e e bokoa mo dikantorong tse dingwe.

src: timphawu letingekho ezingeni emahhovisi.
tgt: ■ tsela e e sa lolamang ya go laola mela.

src: umlimi longumake uli ma indlela yakhe leya emphumelelweni nonkululeko mathebula kusuka ebuphuyeni nekutsi bameye ngenca yekusebenta epulasini mahlatse matlakane (loneminyaka yebudzala le20) manje ungumlimi wephepha leluhlata satjani lomama tsekako.
tgt: molemi wa mosadi o lema tsela ya gagwe ya katlego nonkululeko mathebula go golela mo bohu meng le go tshegiwa ka go bo a dira mo po laseng, mahlatse matlakane (20) ga jaana ke molemi yo o tletseng monyebo yo a le mang pherefere e tala.

src: mahlatse wacala ngeku volontiya kusebenta ngetimphelansontfo nangemaholide esikolwa epulasini lendzawo lelilima iphepha leluhlata satjani aneminyaka le15 kute asite make wakhe ngekutsi batfole lokuya etfunjini.

src: ngemuva kwekubona inchubekelembili yakhe epulasini lanel sikhulu sendzawo sabese simupha umhlaba longemahektha lange40 epulasini ibabirwa ba tau ya tswala lapho khona manje sekusepulasini lakhe lalima kulo.

src: libutfo letemvelo livikela bobhejanes dale hes umelusi wetemvelo phakamani nyawo (loneminyaka yebudzala le26), lotinte esichiwini semvelo eumkhuze game reserve kwazuluna tal, ungulumumye webelu si laba1 659 temapaki ave lonkhe aseningizimu afrika (isanparks) lebanike umse benti wekunakekela imvelo etichiwini tekonga imvelo ta hulumende netangasese kuyo yonkhe iningizimu afrika.
tgt: marenjara a sireletsa ditshukudu dale hes motlhokomedi wa tikologo phakamani nyawo (26), yo a direlang kwa serapeng sa diphologolo sa umkhuze kwa kwazulunatal, ke mongwe wa batlhokomedi ba le 1 659 bao diphaka tsa bosetšhaba tsa aforika borwa (sanparks) di beileng tshepo mo go bona go tlhokomela tikologo mo dira peng tsa tlhago tsa setšhaba le tsa poraefete go ralala aforika borwa.

src: nyawo, loyincenye yemklamo wekulandzela temvelo lochutjwa yiepwp , ukholelwa ekutsi kubalulekile kufundzisa imimango mayelana nekunakekelwa kwemvelo.
tgt: nyawo, yo e leng karolo ya porojeke ya go tlhokomela tikologo eo e tsamaisiwang ke epwp , o dumela gore go botlhokwa go ruta baagi ka ga go tlhokomela tikologo.

src: "sifanele kutsi sihambe siyo fundzisa imimango futsi siyente ivisise kutsi kungani kubalule kile kutsi kongiwe imvelo.
tgt: "re tlhoka go ya kwa baaging le go ba tlhalosetsa gore ke goreng go le botlhokwa go babalela tlhago.

src: ngu laphoke ummango utawuvisisa kutsi indzima ledlalwa tilwane tasendle", kwasho yena.
tgt: ke fela seo se tla dirang gore ba tlhaloganye botlhokwa jwa tlhago," a rialo.

src: loluhlelo, loluhlomisa bantfu labasha baseningizimu afri ka ngemakhono labawadzingako kute bakwati kusebenta etindzaweni tekonga imvelo nekuhlalisana kwetilwanyana netihlahla, sewente sicinise ko sekutsi nyawo uyakhona kunakekela umndeni wakhe.
tgt: lenaane leno, leo le nayang bašwa ba aforika borwa bokgo ni jo ba bo tlhokang go dira kwa mafelong a pabalelo ya tlhago le dimela mmogo le ditshedi tse di farologaneng, le netefa ditse gore nyawo o kgona go tlhokomela balelapa la gagwe.

src: "luphahla lwendlu lelikhaya lemndeni wami manje seyifule lwe kahle kakhulu, alusavuti, futsi loko kungenca yemsebenti wami.
tgt: "ka ntlha ya tiro ya me, ntlo ya lapa la me jaanong e na le dithulelo tse di ntle tse ebile di sa neleng.

src: kuyangitfokotsa kutsi ngatfola lelitfuba," kwasho yena.
tgt: ke motlotlo gore ke bo ke bone tšhono eno," a rialo.

src: indvuna yelitiko letemve lo dkt.
tgt: tona ya merero ya tikologo ngaka edna molewa o bitsa batlhokomedi bano 'marenjara' gonne ba tshameka karolo e e botlhokwa mo go lwantsheng bosenyi jwa tikologo, jaaka go bolawa ga ditshukudu.

src: edna molewa sewetse balandzele ligama lebujaha le litsi 'libutfo letemvelo' ngoba badlala umsebenti lomkhulu ekulweni nebugebengu, njenge kutingela kubulawe bobhejane ngalokungekho emtsetfweni.
tgt: "ngogola batlhokomedi ba tikologo ba le 1 659 ba ne ba romelwa kwa mafelong ao go bolawang ditshukudu ka bontsi go thusa ka tshireletso ya tikolo go.

src: "kulomnyaka lophelile kwakhishwa balandzeleli be temvelo la1 659 bayiswa etindzaweni letihamba embili ekutingelweni kubuye kubu lawe bobhejane ngalokungekho emtsetfweni kute bayokweleke lela ekuvikelweni kwemvelo.
tgt: ba tla natlafatswa go nna baambasatara ba ditshukudu mo dikgaolong tseno," a rialo.

src: luhlelo lwekudala imisebenti luvutsa emalangabi adele schormann working on fire (wof) ilawula luhlelo loluhlanganisile lwekulawula imililo lodalela imisebenti yebantfu labasha labanyenti labavela emimangweni lephuyile.
tgt: lenaane le le ikemiseditse go tlhama ditiro adele schormann working on fire (wof) e tsamai sa lenaane le le tshwaraganetsweng la botsa maisi jwa molelo leo le nete faditseng ditiro go bašwa ba le bantsi go tswa kwa baaging bao go neng go ikgatolositswe bone.

src: ngekwesekelwa ngetima li litiko letemvelo, loluhlelo luwela ngaphasi kweluhlelo lwetemisebenti yahulumende leyengetiwe (iepwp).
tgt: lenaane leno, leo le neelwang matlole ke le fapha la merero ya tikologo, le wela ka fa tlase ga lenaanekatoloso la ditiro tsa setšhaba (epwp).

src: luniketa litsemba kulusha lolunyenti lolungatfoli imisebenti futsi selube nemphumelelo lencomeka kakhulu ekuvikeleni nasekulawuleni imililo yesiganga, lunciphisa lifutse lwayo.
tgt: gape le neetse bašwa ba le bantsi bao ba sa kgoneng go bona tiro tsholofelo le go fitlhe lela katlego e e makatsang mo go thibeleng le mo go laoleng melelo ya naga, ka go fokotsa ditlamorago tsa ona.

src: loluhlelo lucasha bantfu la bangetulu kwalaba5 000 la bavela emimangweni lephuyile luphindze futsi lubaceceshe kutekwati ngemlilo, temfundvo kanye nekuwucindzetela nala manye emakhono, njengelusito lwekucala, kubata, kupheka, temphilo netekuphepha kanye netekuchumana.
tgt: lenaane leno le thapa batho ba feta ba le 5 000 go tswa kwa baaging bao go neng go ikga tolositswe bone le go ba katisa ka ga tsibogelo ya molelo, thu to ka molelo, thibelo le taolo ya molelo mmogo le ka bokgoni jo bongwe, jo bo jaaka thuso ya potlako, go dira ka legong, go apaya, boitekanelo le pabalese go le ditlhaeletsano.

src: sikhulu setekuchuma sewof lebogang maseko uchaze watsi loluhlelo luhlose bantfu labasha luphindze futsi lucasha bantfu labakhubatekile kutsi base bente etikhungweni talo letisetifundzeni.
tgt: sebueledi sa wof lebogang maseko o tlhalositse gore le naane leno le tsepile bašwa le go thapa batho ba ba nang le dikgwetlho tsa mmele go dira kwa ditheong tsa bona tse di kwa di porofenseng.

src: "sigcizelelaka kakhulu kutfutfukisa emakhono nekuni ka lusha imisebenti, lusha lolu sha loluvela etikolweni temabanga laphakeme noma lolusandza kuphotfula etikhungweni temfundvo lephakeme.
tgt: "re gatelela thata mo tlhabo lolong ya bokgoni le go neela ditiro go bašwa bao ba sa tswang go konosetsa dithuto tsa bone tsa sekolo se segolwane kgotsa bao ba sa tswang go aloga go tswa kwa ditheong tsa thuto e kgolwane.

src: kubaceceshwa balohlulelo, labange ma94% ngebantfu labasha, la bange31% bomake bese kutsi labayi3% ngebantfu labakhu batekile," washo acinisekisa.
tgt: go bao ba leng mo lenaenong leno, 94% ya bone ke bašwa, 31% ya bone ke basadi mme diperesente di le tharo tsa bone ba na le dikgwetlho mo mmeleng," a netefatsa.

src: lorraine mokoena (lone minyaka yebudzala le31) wase mpumalanga ungulomunye webaceceshwa lowazuza kulo luhlelo.

src: mokoena wacala alijuniya lesicimamlilo futsi sewusebente ngekutikhandla wakhuphu ka waba ngumholi lomkhulu welicembu lebacimimlilo, uhola licembu lebacimimlilo laba18.

src: "lomsebenti uyintjintjile imphilo yami.

src: ngimi kuphela lo nesibopho salokuya etfunjini se bantfwana bakitsi nebantfwana bami lababili.
tgt: ke nna fela ke tlamelang bonnake le banake ba babedi.

src: manje ngiyakhona kondla umndeni wami ngiyise nebantfwana bami esikolweni," kwasho mokoena.
tgt: jaanong ke kgona go fepa bale lapa la me le go tsenya banake sekolo," ga rialo mokoena.

src: "ukuvumile kutsi lomsebenti wekucima umlilo ngalokwetayelekile ungumsebenti wemadvodza futsi sewufundze kutsi acine abe nemandla ku lomkhakha.
tgt: o dumetse gore tiro ya go tima molelo ka gale ke tiro ya banna mme jaaka mosadi mo ti rong eno o ithutile go nna segatlhamelamasisi.

src: mokoena uphokophele ekube ni ngumphatsi wemisebenti yemacembu kuleminyaka lemibili letako.
tgt: mokoena o beile mogopolo wa gagwe mo go nneng motsamai si wa ditiragatso mo sebakeng sa dingwaga di le pedi tse di latelang.

src: loku kutawumenta kutsi abe nesibopho sawo onkhe emacembu ewof lase mphumalanga.
tgt: seno se tla mo rwesa maikarabelo a ditlhopha tsotlhe tsa wof kwa mpumalanga.

src: njengoba naku sesifikelwe sikhatsi semililo, mokoena unikete lamasu ekuvikela imililo yesiganga lalandzelako: ungalumeki imililo endzaweni levulekile uma ngabe angeke ukhone kuwu lawula.
tgt: ka setlha sa melelo se re apa retse, mokoena o neelane ka maele a a latelang go thibela melelo ya dikgwa: o seka wa besa molelo mo mpaananeng fa o ka se kgone go o laola.

src: yenta siciniseko sekutsi une lusito netisetjentiswa letenele tekubukana nato tonkhe timo.
tgt: netefatsa gore o na le thuso e e lekaneng le didiriswa tse di tshwanetseng go go thusa fa go ka nna le matsapa ape.

src: ungawushiyi umlilo unga kagadvwa.
tgt: o seka wa tlogela molelo o tuka o le nosi.

src: caphela simo selitulu.
tgt: tlhokomela maemo a bosa.

src: kugucula temfundvo lephakeme amukelani chauke imfundvo lephakeme eningizimu afrika iyagucuka, akusiko kuphela kutsi sekulula ku tfola imfundvo lephakeme kodvwa futsi utfola leco ndziswe kahle kutsi imelane netidzingo tetimboni.
tgt: go fetola lephata la thuto e kgolwane amukelani chauke seemo sa thuto e kgo lwane ya aforika borwa mo nageng se a fetoga, mme thuto e kgo lwane ga se fela gore e a fi tlhelesega, mme gape le gore jaanong e lepalepane le di tlhokwa tsa intaseteri.

src: leti ngucuko timcoka ngoba live letfu lisebenta kulungiselela bantfu labasha kute bame lane nemisebenti nekufaka sandla kutemnotfo.
tgt: di phetogo tseno di botlhokwa ka gonne naga e ipaakanye tsa go baakanyetsa bašwa go ka simolola go tsena mo ma felong a bodirelo le go nna le seabe mo ikonoming.

src: njengoba sive sigubha inya nga yelusha, ivuk’uzenzele ibukisisa indlela lusha lwale live luniketwa ngayo ema tfuba ekuphumelela litiko letemfundvo lephakeme nekucecesha.
tgt: jaaka naga e keteka se gopotso sa kgwedi ya ba šwa, vuk’uzenzele e lebele la ntlha ya ka fao bašwa ba naga eno ba tlamelwang ke lefapha la thuto e kgolwane le katiso ka ditšhono ka teng gore ba atlege.

src: naledi pandor, indvuna yetemfundvo lephakeme nekucecesha lebekwe ngendlovana iniketwe u msebenti wekungenisa luhle lo lwemfundvo lephakeme yamahhala kulabo laba phuyile kanye nalabafundzi labavela kumindeni lehola imali lengetulu kwelizinga lelibekiwe kepha labasolo bangakhoni kukhokhela ti ndleko tasenyuvesi.
tgt: fa e sale a thapilwe mo kgwe ding ya tlhakole mono ngwaga jaaka tona ya thu to e kgolwane le katiso, naledi pandor o neilwe tiro ya go diragatsa thuto e e sa lefelelweng go thusa baithuti ba ba humanegileng le "bao letseno la kwa mala peng a bo bona le sa ba kgo ntsheng go ka tlamelwa ka matlole a nsfas".

src: emva kwesiteleka lesidze savelonkhe ngaphansi kwesihloko lesitsi: #fees mustfall, kwamenyetelwa ngengongoni kutsi lusha loluvela kumindeni lehola imali lengaphansi kwer350 000 ngemnyaka lutawu tfola imfundvo yemazinga laphakeme nekuceceshwa yamahhala.
tgt: morago ga boipelaetso jwa naga ka bophara jo bo tsereng nako e telele, ka setlhogo se se reng #feesmustfall , ka kgwedi ya sedimonthole go ne ga tlhagisiwa fa bašwa ba ba tswang mo malapeng ao letseno la bo bona le leng ka fa tlase ga r350 000 ka ngwaga ba tla amogela thu to le katiso e kgolwane ntle le go ntsha le ka peni o mo ntsho.

src: kuphake lwa kwalemfundvo kusachubeka fu tsi kutawutsatsa sikhatsi lesinge tulu kwemi nyaka lesihla nu.
tgt: tsenyotirisong e tswe letse mme e tla diraga diwa mo pakeng ya di ngwaga di le tlhano.

src: luhlelo lwemfundzateindvuna pandor icinisekise kutsi kungeniswa kweluhlelo lwemfundzate kuchubeka kahle.
tgt: sekema sa dibasari "tona pandor o dirile netefaletso ya fa tiragatso ya sekema sa dibasari e tswelela sentle ntle le kgoreletso epe.

src: "loluhlelo lolusha lwemfu ndzate likungenelela loku mcoka kwahulumende wase ningizimu afrika, ngoba, ecinisweni, bantfu baseningi zimu afrika imali yabo yentse la lekhokhela lemifundzate," washo njalo.
tgt: "sekema se se ntšhwa seno sa dibasari ke kgatotsereganyo e e botlhokwa thata ya puso ya aforika borwa, mmogo le baagi ba aforika borwa ka gonne ke makgetho a bona a a duelelang seno" o rialo.

src: loluhlelo lwemfundzate luni ketwa labo bafundzi labacala kungena emanyuvesi kanye nasemakolishi etifundvo te buciko bemisebenti yetandla kanye nekuceceshwa (ematvet), kuyo yonkhe iminyaka yekufundza.
tgt: sekema seno sa dibasari se neelwa baithuti ba ba tsenang yunibesithi la ntlha le baithuti ba ba kwa dikholetšheng tsa thuto le katiso ya tiro ya matso go le ya setegeniki (ditvet), mo dingwageng tsotlhe tsa fa ba ntse ba le mo dithutong.

src: lomfundzate wesekelwe nge mali leyengetiwe yahulume nde letigidzigidzi letir7.166 ngemnyaka we2018 – kwatsi tigidzigidzi ler4.581 tabeke lwa bafundzi labaphumelele kungena emanyuvesi kwatsi tigidzigidzi ler2.585 tabeke lwa bafundzi bemakolishi etvet.
tgt: go tlamela sekema seno sa dibasari ka matlole, puso e tlametse lefapha ka madi a mangwe gape a le kanaka r7.166 bilione ya yona mo ngwageng wa 2018 – mme r4.581 bilione ya yona e bee tswe thoko go thusa baithuti ba dipholo tsa bona di ba letlang go ithuta kwa diyunibesithing, mme r2.585 bilione ya yona e tla nna ya baithuti ba dipholo tsa bona di ba letlang go ithuta mo ditvet.

src: indvuna pandor yatsi ema kolishi labukene nemikhakha letsite yetemfundvo angahle abe tikhungo tebuchwephesha letikhicita emakhono lancono kulowo mkhakha wesifundvo.
tgt: tona pandor o rile dikholetšhe tse dirutwa tsa tsona di dirang ka lephata le le rileng fela la thuto, di ka nna mafelo a bo tswerere a a tsamaelanang le go tlhagisa bokgoni jo bo maemo a a kwa godimo mo lephateng le ba tla bong ba dira ka lona.

src: sibonelo, likolishi lelilodvwa lingabukana kuphela nemse benti webunjiniyela betinjini bese kutsi lelinye libukane nebunjiniyela kutetindiza, wa chaza njalo.
tgt: sekai, kholetšhe e e rileng e ka ruta dithuto tsa mechanical engineering mme e nngwe e rute fela dithuto tsa ditiro tsa phofiso ya difofane, o tlhalosi tse jalo.

src: wangeta ngekutsi "ngiyatsemba kutsi kuvumela kutsi likolishi libukane kuphela netifundvo letitsite letimba lwa kulikusasa lemakolishi.
tgt: "ke dumela gore boka moso jwa dikholetšhe bo mo diatleng tsa go dira ka serutwa se le sengwe," o ne a tlaleletsa ka go rialo.

src: asifuni kutsi onkhe ente intfo lefanako.
tgt: ga re batle go bona dikho letšhe tsotlhe tsa rona di dira selo se se tshwanang.

src: "kusesenjalo luhlelo lwemfu ndvo lephakeme lwekutfu tfukisa bosomabhizinisi lasu ngulwa lomnyaka lophelile kute kugcugcutelwe bantfu la basha bacale amabhizinisi abo.
tgt: "mo lenaanethutong la thuto e kgolwane, go thankgolotswe tsweletsopele ya bogwebi mo ngwageng o o fetileng go ro tloetsa bašwa go itshimololela dikgwebo tse e leng tsa bona.

src: ummango ugubha umkhosi wesivumelwano sekubuyiselwa umhlaba setigidzigidzi letinger21 siya miti ummango wase mphumalanga kapa utawungenelela emkhakheni wetichiwu tetilwane tasendle ngemuva kwekutsi utfole kusekelwa ngetimali nguhulumende kutsi basungule luhlelo lwekulawula sichiwu setinya matane.
tgt: baagi ba keteka tumelano ya lefatshe ya bokanaka r21 milione siya miti baagi ba kwa kapa bo tlhaba ba ipaakanye ditse go dira ka natla morago ga gore ba tlamelwe ka matlole gore ba gape kwa pele lenaane le le gapiwang ke baagi la taolo ya dirapa tsa diphologolo.

src: lommango wasedouble drift dvutane nasegrahamstown uhlala bantfu labalinganiselwa ku1 500 labavela emindenini le264.

src: lommango usandza kutfola tincwadzi tebuniyo talomhlaba, lewabuyiselwa kubo ngekwa loluhlelo lekwabiwa kabusha kwemhlaba.

src: ngekusho kwandvunankhulu wasemphumalanga koloni phumulo masualle, imali etigidzi letinger21 seyibeke lwe kutsi kutsengwe lomhlaba kantsi utawubuyiselwa kuba nikati ngekwetigaba.
tgt: "eno ke kgato e kgologadi fa go tla mo tshomarelong ya tlha go le mo phetolothefosanong ya beng ba naga.

src: lesichiwu siyatfutfu kiswa kutsi sikwati kuncinti sana kahle naletinye tichiwu tetilwane tasendle kantsi hulumende usekela lommango ngekubaniketa imali, tilwane tasendle nelucecesho," kusho masualle.

src: lommango, lebalawula nawo lesichiwu ngekusebentisana neeastern cape parks and tourism agency (iecpta) ngapha nsi kwelikhayalethu com munal property association (ilcpa), batfole imali letigidzi ler6 levela kulitiko letemvelo kutsi basungule umkhakha wekukhulisa umnotfo ngetasendle kulesichiwu lesinemahekta la 1 400 lebatsengelwe sona litiko lekutfutfukiswa kwetindzawo tasemaphandleni netingucuku kutemhlaba.
tgt: baagi bano, ba ba laolang serapa seno sa diphologolo tsa naga ka tshwaraganelo le setheo sa bojanala sa diphaka tsa kapa botlhaba (ecpta) ka fa tlase ga leina la likhayalethu communal property asso­ciation (lcpa), ba amogetse r6 milione go tswa kwa le fapheng la merero ya tikologo gore ba dire letsholo la dikgwebo tsa dirapa tsa diphologolo tsa naga mo serapeng seno sa diphologolo tsa naga sa bogolo jo bo kanaka diheketara di le 1 400 seo ba se reketsweng ke lefapha la tlhabololo ya metseselegae le ntšhwafatso ya naga.

src: sihlalo welcpa, mxolisi ngesi, utsite lommango wenta sicelo sekubuyiselwa umhlaba nga1998.

src: bosotimboni bemakhemikhali labamnyama basefreyistata bakha ematfuba emsebenti more matshediso inkhapani yakule ndzawo lekhicita ema khemikhali iyasi ta ekulweni nekuswe lekala kwematfuba emse benti ngekutsi yakhe ema tfuba emsebenti lasimeme lalinganiselwa kuma70 endzaweni yaseharrismith, efreyistata.
tgt: beng ba indaseteri ya dikhemikhale ba bathobatsho kwa foreisetata ba tlhola ditiro more matshediso setlamo sa fa gae sa go apaya dikhe mikhale se thu sa go lwantsha bo tlhokatiro ka go tlhama ditiro di ka nna di le 70 kwa harri smith kwa foreisetata.

src: ikevali chemicals yinkhapani yekucala lephetfwe ba ntfu labamnyama kulendzawo yasefreyistata lekhicita imihlo bo lehlukene yemakhemikhali ekucwenga emanti, ekuhlobisa endlini nekuhlanta imithoyi kanye nekwekunamatselisa.
tgt: kevali chemicals ke setlamo sa ntlha sa bathobatsho se se apayang dikhemikhale tse di farologaneng tse di tlhatswang metsi, tse di phepafatsang le tse di phepafatsang mafelo a kgele loleswe le tse di kgomaretsang.

src: lenkhapani yasungulwa nga2014 bangani labasihlanu labanelwati ngemakhemikhali, timphahla letitsengiseka masi nyane, kutfutfukiswa kwe mikhicito, kanye netinhlobo letahlukene teglu yekunama tselisa.
tgt: setlamo seno se simolotswe ka ngwaga wa 2014 ke ditsala di le tlhano tse di nang le kitso e e tseneletseng mo maphateng a dikhemikhale, a go thota dilo tse di rekisiwang, a go rulaganya dilo tse di rekisiwang le a go dira dikgomaretsi.

src: umcondzisi lomkhulu wekevali chemicals funeka khumalo utsi ibis yasekela inkhapani yakhe kutsi itfole imishini nemathulusi kute icale kukhicita nekusungula umkhi cito wekucwenga emanti, weku hlobisa nekubulala emagci wane kanye netinhlobonhlobo teglu yekunamatselisa.
tgt: mokaedikhuduthamaga wa kevali chemicals funeka khumalo a re bis e tshegeditse setlamo sa gagwe gore a kgone go simolola ka tlhagisodikuno le go rekisa dikhemikhale tsa go tlhatswa meetsi, go phepafatsa le go peita ditshenekegi mmogo le tsa go kgomaretsa.

src: "uma sicala kwafanele kwekutsi sifake imali kute lebhizi nisi icale kusebenta kodvwa sabese sesitfola kusekelwa ngetimali belitiko letekuhwe belana netimboni (idti) ngekusebentisa ibis kanye nenhlangano yekutfutfukisa timboni (iidc)," asho anaba.
tgt: "kwa tshimologong re ne ra gapeletsega gore re tsenye madi gore kgwebo eno e simolole go dira fela kwa bofelong re ne ra amogela matlole go tswa kwa lefapheng la kgwebisano le inta seteri (dti) ka bis mmogo le ka koporasi ya tlhabololo ya diintaseteri (idc)," o ne a tlaleletsa jalo.

src: ibis iluhlelo lwesibonelelo salenchubomgomo yaboso timboni labamnyama lehlose kuvula ematfuba lakhona kubosotimboni labamnyama eninizimu afrika ngekusebe ntisa indlela yekungenelela noma njani ngetimali nanga lokunye lokungadzingi imali, ngendlela lehlosiwe futsi lecha zwe kahle.
tgt: sekema seno ke lenaane la tlamelokamatlole la pholisi ya diintaseteri tsa bathobatsho leo maitlhomo a lona e leng go bulela ditšhono mo diintasetering tsa bathobantsho tse di direlang ikonomi ya naga ya aforika borwa ka ditsereganyo tse di tlhamaletseng, tse di totileng diintaseteri tse di rileng e bile di itlhalosa ka botlalo mo dithu song tsa matlole le mo tseo e seng tsa matlole.

src: khumalo utsi kwabatsatsa imali lelinganiselwa kutigidzi ler18 kutsi lebhizinisi ikhone kucala kusebenta netinyanga letilinganiselwa ku11 kutsi bacale kwenta inzuzo.
tgt: khumalo a re e mo tsere bokanaka r18 milione gore a simolole kgwebo eno mmogo le dikgwedi di ka feta di le 11 gore a simolole go ka iponela morokotso go tswa mo kgwebong eno.

src: lenkhapani isabalalisa imikhicito yayo kuyo yonkhe iningi zimu afrika kanye naseuganda, namibia, nasetanzania.
tgt: setlamo seno se rekisa ditlhagisiwa tsa sona mo nageng yotlhe ya aforika borwa mmogo le kwa nageng ya uganda, ya namibia, le ya tanzania.

src: khumalo utse lomtselela lenkhapani lebe nawo etimphi lweni tebantfu bendzawo mkhulu kunekwakha ematfuba emsebenti.
tgt: khumalo a re seabe seo se tlamo seno se nang le sona mo matshelong a baagi se segolo thata go feta le sa ditšhono tsa diphatlhatiro.

src: "kuko konkhe nalokungetulu kwekwakha ematfuba emsebe nti kubantfu bendzawo, sinelu hlelo lwekusisa emmangweni lapho sisita khona bomake basemadolobheni nasemakhaya kutsi batisungulele emabhi zinisi lasemancane lasebenta ngekukhicita imikhicito yekuhlobisa nekucoceka emakhaya," asho alandzisa.
tgt: "mo godimo ga go tlhola ditiro mo baaging ba tikologo, re na gape le lenaane le le beeleditseng mo setšhabeng ka lona re thusa basadi ba kwa makeišeneng le ba kwa metseselegaeng gore ba kgone go ipulela dikgwebopotlana tsa bona tse di dirang ka go ikaapela didirisiwa tsa go phepafatsa mo malapeng le ditlhagisiwa tsa phepafatso ya kgelelaleswe," o tlaleleditse jalo.

src: kwakha ematfuba emsebenti elusha lwasekzn hlengiwe ngobese bantfu labasha laba linganiselwa kuma20 labavela kwazu lunatal balindzeleke kutsi bahlomule embonini lensha yakamahindra lebite imali letigidzi letinger95 leta wube yakha luhlobo lolusha lwemaveni angemadouble cab labitwa ngemapik up ngaphandle nje kancane kwasedurban.

src: sikhulu lesiphetse temisebenti mhlabawonkhe sakamahindra arvind ma tthew utsi lenkhapani ihlose kutsenga ma40% waletinye tetintfo talamaveni emapik up kutitolo takuleli.

src: uma imphilo ikunika emalamula, walime amukelani chauke litiko letekulima lasenshonalanga kapa lichuba luhle lo lolusita balimi labasha nalasebabomnkantjubovu ngeluhlelo lwekusita kusu kela kucalwa nje ngelilanga lekucala – uma badzinga lusito lwemali – kute kube ngulapho nabo sebakhona kutimela.
tgt: fa botshelo bo go naya ratsuru, jala dithapo tsa yone amukelani chauke lefapha la temothuo la kwa kapa bophirima le tsamaisa lenaane le le thusang balemirui ba bantšhwa le bao e leng kgale ba lema ka go ba tshegetsa go tloga motsing wa ntlha – fa ba tlhoka tlamelo ya ma tlole – go fitlha ba kgona go ikemela ka bobone.

src: loluhlelo lwekusita ne kutfutfukisa balimi selusite bantfu labasha njenga wayne mansfield (lone minyaka lenge33 budzala) wasepaarl, losuke ekube ni ngusitolosiyandzindza lobekatsengisela malume wakhe emakethe yasekapa ngesikhatsi asafundza siko lwa watsengisa ngephandle kweminyele yakuleli laseni gizimu afrika emalamula lawalima yena ngekwakhe emhlabeni lawurentako.
tgt: lenaane la tshegetso le tlhabololo ya balemirui leno le thusitse batho ba ba jaaka wayne mansfield (33) wa kwa paarl, yo a neng a rekisetsa malomagwe kwa marakeng wa motsekapa fa dikolo di tswaletse, mo nakong ya fa a ne a santse a tsena sekolo, mme ga ja anong o romela diratsuru tsa gagwe kwa dinageng tsa kwa ntle tseo a di lemileng mo polaseng eo ba mo hiri seditseng yona.

src: eminyakeni lelishumi le yendlulile, ngesikhatsi angusomabhizinisi lone minyaka lenge23 budzala, mansfield wala litfuba leku sebenta epulazini lebeka cupha kulo emalamula bese uyawatsengisa.
tgt: dingwaga di le 10 tse di fetileng, fa a ne a le dingwa ga di le 23 mme a setse a itshi moletse kgwebo, mansfield o ne a gana tšhono ya go dira kwa polaseng eo a neng rwa la diratsuru kwa go yona go di rekisa.

src: kwengeta ekutsini bekasesemncane futsi ete nenkhabunkhabu yekulima.

src: "ngaphindze ngacaphela kutsi balimi nabo bebenta loku bekwentiwa ngitsi tsi ne bositolosiyandzindza – bebatipakishela imikhicito yabo bese bayoyitsengisa emakethe ekapa.
tgt: "ke ne ka lemoga gape gore balemirui ba dira seo rona barekisi re se dirang – ba ne ba phuthela ditholwana tsa bona mme ba di rekisa kwa marakeng wa motsekapa.

src: nga2015, wakhona kutse ngisa emalamula lange mathani lange31 ngapha ndle kweminyele yale li laseningizimu afrika kwaphindze futsi kwatsi nga2016, lelinani lakhula kakhulu laba ngemathani la168.
tgt: ka ngwaga wa 2015, o ne a setse a kgona go romela kwa ntle ditone di le 31 tsa ratsuru mme palo eno e ne ya menagana thata go ka nna ditone di le 168 ka ngwaga wa 2016. seno ke ka ditebogo go tswa mo katisong le thu song eo a e neilweng ke ba lenaane la tshegetso le tlhabololo ya balemirui e leng seo se mo kgontshitseng gore a amogele madithuso a lenaane la tshegetso ya te mothuo ka botlalo (casp) ka ngwaga wa 2015, mme seno se ne sa mo kgontsha gore a tsetsepele thata le go atlega jaaka molemirui.

src: aaron motsoaledi utsi umtsetfosivivinyo wekuchibela tindzaba te mshwalensi wavelonkhe we temphilo (inhi) utawenta kancono lizinga letinsita te temphilo eningizimu afrika.

src: motsoaledi bekakhuluma emhlanganweni webetindza ba losandza kubanjwa lapho beketfula khona umtsetfo sivivinyo wekuchitjelwa kwetindzaba tenhi kanye nemtsetfosivivinyo wekuchi bela tindzaba tetikimu tete kwelashwa.
tgt: melaotlhomo eno e tla baakanya tsela gore tlho komelo ya boitekanelo e fitlhe lesege bonolo ka nhi.

src: umtsetfosivivinyo luhlaka lwemtsetfo.

src: imitsetfosivivi nyo leminyeti yentiwa litiko lahulumende ngekucondzi swa yindvuna lefanele.

src: lomtse tfosivivinyo ufanele kutsi ubese uvunywa yikhabhine thi ngembi kwekutsi wetfulwe ephalamende.
tgt: molaotlhomo o tshwanetswe gore o amoge lwe ke kabinete pele o ka isi wa kwa palamenteng.

src: lokwetfulwa kwalemitse tfosivivinyo lemibili kusho kutsi inigizimu afrika seyi dvute ngesinyatselo sinye ekutsini itfole tekunakekelwa kwebantfu ngelizinga lelihle letemphilo ngalokufananako lokusho kutsike masinyane nje inhi itawuba ngumtse tfo.
