tgt: go ya ka zulu, lephata la dikgogo ke lephata le lengwe la a a botlhokwa ka fa nageng, go nne malapa a le mantsi a ja nama ya kgogo go phala dinama tse dingwe.

src: zulu, tinkhukhu tingumkhakha lomcoka kakhulu kulelive, ngobe imindeni leminyenti idla tinkhukhu kwengca nome ngabe nguluphi luhlobo lwenyama.
tgt: ngaka zulu o fisegela gore ngwaga yo mongwe le yo mongwe a ka katisa basadi ba feta ba le 1 000 ka tsa temo go ralala le naga.

src: utimisele futsi ngekutsi abe ngulomunye webakhiciti labatsembekile lapha eningizimu afrika wetinkhukhu letingagcinwa ehhokweni sonkhe sikhatsi netibhidvo temvelo.
tgt: o tsewa gape jaaka molemirui yo a tshepagalang wa nama ya dikgogo tse di bulelwang gore di ye go sela le motlhagisi wa merogo e e sa godisiweng ka dikhemikhale.

src: weluleka bomake labanesifiso sekulima kutsi bacale kancane futsi bangalindzeli kwesekelwa nguhulumende.
tgt: o eletsa balemirui ba basadi ba ba fisegelang go nna balemirui gore ba se itlhaganele mme ba tseye kgato ka kgato mme ba se letele gore puso e ba tswe thuso.

src: "nangabe kwesekwela nguhulumende kukutfola, kutawuba kukufukula lokwengetiwe.
tgt: "thuso ya puso fa e tla e tshwanetse go go fitlhela o setse o le kgakala.

src: nangabe udzinga kukhicita bobhayizane laba3 000, kute lokukuvimba kutsi ucale nge20.
tgt: fa e le gore o batla go ipona o ruile dikgogo di le 3 000, ga go sepe se se go kgoreletsang gore o simolole ka go rua di le 20. kopana le mabentlele a dijo a magolo a mo o leng gone mme o utlwe gore fa o batla go ba rekisetsa ba tlhoka gore ditlhagisiwa tsa gago di bo di le mo maemong afe a boleng mme lo ipope ngatana gore le kgone go tlhagisa dijo tsa boleng joo le go fitlhelela palo e ba e tlhokang.

src: hamba ucocisane nemasuphamakethe endzawo kute utfole kutsi afuna lizinga lelinjani fusi nisebentisane ngemacembu kute kutsi nihlangabetane netimfuno telizinga nelinani lawo," kwengeta yena njalo.
tgt: go matlafatsa basadi ka temothuongaka zulu o dumela gore temothuo e ka nna le mosola o mogolo mo go direng gore basadi ba itirele letseno le mo go tlholeleng basadi ba bangwe ba bantsi ditiro.

src: "nangabe utfutfukisa make, suke utfutfukisa sive.
tgt: "fa o dira gore mosadi a ikemele o a bo o dira gore setšhaba se ikemele.

src: siyakhona kwabelana ngelwati lwetfu sente futsi kutsi bantfu labanyenti batimbandzakanye.
tgt: re le basadi re kgona go abelana ka kitso e re nang le yona le go dira gore seo se tswele molemo batho ba bangwe ba bantsi.

src: "wengeta ngekutsi bomake kufanele kutsi bangagcini kuphela ngekulima kodvwa kudzingeka kutsi bahlole naletinye tindlela tekusebenta talemboni letifanana nekusebenta imikhitito yetekulima, kufaka emaphakethini kanye nekutsengisa futsi.
tgt: "o tlaleleditse ka gore basadi ga ba tshwanela go itomeletsa ka go dira tiro ya temothuo fela mme ba tshwanetse go dira ditiro tse dingwe tse di sa tlwaelegang tsa intaseteri eno go tshwana le go tsena mo kgwebong ya go rekisa dijo tse di apeilweng tse di kotutsweng, ya go phuthela dilwana tse di kotutsweng le ya go reka ba rekisa dilo tse di kotutsweng.

src: "kutimela ngekwetimali ngiyo kuphela intfo le ngasita kucedza lobudlova lobucondziswe ebulilini lobutsite futsi loko kungafezekiswa ngekutsi kusetjentiswe kulima, emkhatsini walokunye," kwasho dkt.
tgt: "go itirela letseno ke yona tsela ya tse dingwe tse di ka dirisiwang go fedisa tirisodikgoka e e totileng batho ba bong jo bo rileng mme seno, gare ga ditiro tse dingwe tse dintsi, se ka kgona go diragadiwa ka ditiro tsa temothuo," ga rialo ngaka zulu.

src: emabhizinisi lamancane ayagcugcutelwa kutsi afake ticelo tekusekelwanosihle shelembe indvuna yetekutfu tfukisa emabhizinisi lamancane, stella ndabeniabrahams, ugcugcutele emabhizinisi lamancane emalokishini nasetindzaweni tasema khaya kutsi afake ticelo tekwesekelwa ngekusebentisa luhlelo lwete mabhizinisi asemalokishi nasetindzaweni tasemakhaya (itrep).
tgt: go ikuelwa mo dikgwebopotlaneng gore di tsenye dikopo tsa go enngwa nokengnosihle shelembe tona ya tlhabololo ya dikgwebopotla na, stella ndabe niabrahams, o ikuetse mo dikgwebopotlaneng kwa makeišeneng le kwa me tseselegaeng gore di tse nye dikopo tsa go enngwa nokeng ka go sola moso la letsholo la go ema nokeng boitshimololedi kgwebo kwa makeišeneng le kwa metseselegaeng (trep).

src: "sikwenta ngenhloso kutsi silungise kuswelakala kwemisebenti nebuphuya, siphindze futsi sibe nesibopho sekutsi sikhulise umnotfo," kwasho yona njalo indvuna ndabeniabrahams.
tgt: "re ikemiseditse go fedisa botlhokatiro le lehuma mme gape ke maikarabelo a rona go godisa ikonomi," tona ndabeniabrahams o tlhalo sitse jalo.

src: ngesikhatsi akhuluma emhlanganweni welusha weshetradesza lesandza kubanjelwa lapha epitoli, indvuna itsite samba lesikhulu semalimboleko setrep sibe esigidzini semarandi lesinye, incenye yinye iba sibonelomali bese kutsi lenye incenye ibe imalimboleko.
tgt: fa a ne a bua kwa kopanong ya bašwa ya shetradesza e mo malobeng e neng e tshwaretswe kwa pretoria, tona o ne a re madi a mantsi a a beetsweng kwa thoko go samagana le merero ya trep ke milione o le mongwe wa diranta, mme mo go yona go na le lephata le le abelanang ka madithuso fa lephata le lengwe le abelana ka madikadimo.

src: bosomabhizinisi labasetindzaweni tasemakhaya nome emalokishini bangafaka sicelo sekwesekelwa, lokufaka ekhatsi kusekelwa ngetimali, ngekusebentisa lifomu leleteyalekile lelibuya kuejensi yekutfutfukisa emabhizinisi lamancane (iseda), iejensi yetetimali yemabhizinisi lamancane (isefa), iejensi yesikhwa ma savelonkhe sekutfutfu kisa (inef) kanye neejensi yavelonkhe yekutfutfukisa lusha (inyda).
tgt: beng ba dikgwebo tsa ko makeišeneng le tsa ko metseselegaeng ba ka tsenya dikopo tsa go enngwa nokeng, mmogo le tsa go tlamelwa ka madithuso, ka go dirisa foromo ya go dira dikopo e ba ka e fitlhelang mo setheong sa go thusa go godisa dikgwebopotlana (seda), mo setheong sa matlole a dikgwebopotlana (sefa), mo setheong sa naga sa matlole a go godisa dikgwebo (nef) mmogo le mo setheo sa naga sa thuso ya bašwa (nyda).

src: banikati bemabhizinisi kufanele kutsi babe takhamuti taseningizimu afrika.
tgt: gore batho ba bone thuso eno e tshwanetse ya bo e le baagi ba naga ya aforika borwa.

src: letikimi letilandzelako tiyatfolakala kulabo bosomabhizinisi labafanelekako: luhlelo lwekwesekela babhaki betinkhwa nemakhekhe luhlelo lwekusekela kulungiswa kwetimoto kanye netitolo letitsengisa tincenye tetimoto neku khinika timoto (kanye netitolo letincane tetincenye tetimoto naletitimele kanye nabosomabhizinisi betimoto labatimele).
tgt: beng ba dikgwebo tseno ba ka thusiwa ka dithuso tse di latelang: letsholo la go ema nokeng mapaka a ma potlana le a dikuku letsholo la go ema nokeng dikgwebo tsa mafelo a go lokisa le go penta dijanaga (mmogo le dikgwebo le dikgwebopotlana tsa mafelo a a rekisang diphatse tsa dijanaga le dikgwebo tse di potlana tse di sa kwadisiwang tsa go rekisa dijanaga) letsholo la go ema nokeng diselaga letsholo la go ema nokeng dikgwebo tsa diapara, tsa matlalo le tsa masela letsholo la go ema nokeng dikgwebo tsa didirisiwa tsa go itlhokomela letsholo la go ema nokeng dikgwebo tsa dispaza letsholo la go ema nokeng dikgwebo tsa go besa nama le tsa dijo tse di apeilweng.

src: luhlelo lwekwesekela emasilaha luhlelo lwekwesekela labatfunga timphahla tekugcoka, labasebenta ngesikhumba nangendvwangu luhlelo lwekwesekela kuticwala luhlelo lwekwesekela titolo tetisipaza luhlelo lwekwesekela ishisanyama nekudla lokuphekiwekubhalisa kungentiwa ku: smmesa.
tgt: batho ba ka kwadisa mo webesaeteng ya smmesa.

src: za bese uce dzela lwatiso loludzinge kako.
tgt: mme ba tlatse tshedimosetso e e tlhokagalang.

src: kucinisekisa kutsi tinchubo tekutfola timali temabhizinisi lamancane kwenteka ngaphandle kwetihibe futsi kwenteka lula, hulumende umatasatasa ngekuhlanganisa ndzawonye tikhungo temabhizinisi lamancane kutsi akhe iejensi yinye.
tgt: mo go netefatseng gore tlamelo ya matlole ya dikgwebopotlana ga e ngamole tlhogo, puso e samagane le go dira gore ditheo tsotlhe tsa yona tsa dikgwebopotlana e nna setheo se le sengwe fela.

src: "kwanyalo simatasatasa ngenchubo yekuhlanganisa isefa neseda kanye neejensi yekutfutfukisa emabhange lasebentisanako.
tgt: "ga jaanong re samagane le go kopanya sefa le seda mmogo le setheo sa dibanka tsa go thusa dikoporasi.

src: "luhlelo lweshetrades ndabeniabrahams utsite ngekusebentisa imitamo leyehlukahlukene, hulumende usite umkhakha wetemabhizinisi lamancane kutsi ukhule futsi udale kucasheka lokudzingeka kakhulu.
tgt: "letsholo la shetrades ndabeniabrahams o tlhalo sitse gore puso, ka go dirisa matsholo a a farologaneng, e kgonne go tswa thuso lephata la dikgwebopotlana gore le kgone go gola le go tlhola ditiro tse di tlhokagalang.

src: "litiko letekutfutfukisa emabhizinisi lamancane neseda bakhe budle lwane nesikhungo semave emhlaba sekuhweba (iitc), kute kutsi kuletfwe loluhlelo lweshetrades lapha eningizimu afrika kanye nekudala kutsi kube nenkhaba yeshetradesza.
tgt: "ba lefapha la tlhabololo ya dikgwebopotlana mmogo le ba seda ba ikopantse le ba setheo se se botlhokwa sa dikgwebo tsa boditšhabatšhaba (itc), gore letsholo la shetrades le tlisiwe ka fa nageng ya aforika borwa mmogo le go tlhoma lefelo le legolo la shetrades.

src: "loluhlelo luhlose ku tfutfukisa emabhizinisi banikati bawo lababomake kutsi ahwebe lapha eveni, ngekwesigodzi kanye nasemaveni emhlaba.
tgt: "maitlhomo a letsholo leno ke go matlafatsa dikgwebo tse beng ba tsona e leng basadi gore di kgone go gweba ka fa nageng, ka fa kgaolong ya rona ya kontinente le kwa dinageng tsa boditšhabatšhaba.

src: lenkhaba isekela ekuciniseni emakho no etemabhizinisi kanye nekuchudzelana emkha tsini wabosomabhizinisi lababomake baseningizimu afrika lokungenani laba 10 000 esikhatsini lesimi nyaka lemine," kwasho yona njalo indvuna.
tgt: lefelo leno le ema nokeng basadi ba e leng beng ba dikgwebo ba maaforika borwa ba le 10 000 ka dikgato tsa go ba matlafatsa sebaka sa di ngwaga di le nne ka bokgoni jwa go tsamaisa dikgwebo le jwa go dira ka botswapelo," tona o tlhalositse jalo.

src: cishe bosomabhizinisi lababomake baseningizimu afrika la3 000 sebevele babhalisile kushetradesza futsi batfola kufundza ngeinthanethi kwamahhala kanye nekuceceshelwa emakhono ekwenta umsebenti.
tgt: basadi ba ka nna 3 000 ba maaforika borwa ba e leng beng ba dikgwebo ba setse ba ikwadisitse mo go shetradesza e bile jaanong ba tlamelwa ka katiso mo inthaneteng le ka tlhatlhelelo ya bokgoni tse ba sa di dueleleng.

src: leshetradesza itawuphindza futsi yente ncono kutsi kube nekufinyelela lokuncono kulutjalomali kwemabhizinisi laphetfwe bomake kanye nekugcu gcutela ematfuba etemabhi zinisi.
tgt: shetradesza e tla dira gape gore go nne bonolo gore dikgwebo tse beng ba tsona e leng basadi di kgone go fitlhelela dipeeletso mmogo le go oketsa ditšhono tsa dikgwebo.

src: "kutimbandzakanya kwelitiko neseda ku shetradesza kukhombi sa kutinikela kwetfu ekutfutfukiseni kanye nasekucinisekiseni kutfutfukisa ngekwetemnotfo bomake baseningizimu afrika," kwasho indvuna ndabeniabrahams.
tgt: "go nneng le seabe ga rona mo go shetradesza re le lefapha mmogo le seda go bontsha maikemisetso a rona mo go thuseng basadi le mo go reng ba kgone go itirela letseno mo nageng ya aforika borwa," ga rialo tona ndabeniabrahams.

src: singakhona futsi sitawusebenta ngemandla kute sicedze kucishwa kwagezi vukuzenzele unnamed kulamaviki lamba lwa lengcile, ku cishwa kwakhulu kwagezi ngenhloso yekuwonga kutsikamete u mnotfo wetfu futsi kwa banga bulukhuni lobu khulu kubantfu bonkhe baseningizimu afrika.
tgt: go tswa kwa union buildingsre tla dira sengwe le sengwe mo matleng a rona go fedisa go tshaba ga mabone vukuzenzele unnamed e setse e le dibeke di le dintsinyaba mabone a ntse a tshaba a sa fetse mme seo se kgoreletsa tsamaiso ya ikonomi ya naga ya rona le go dira gore maaforika borwa otlhe a rwale boima.

src: sigaba se6 sekucishwa kwagezi ngenhloso yekuwonga kwabangelwa kulahleka kwemamegawatts (emamw) langetulu kwe18 000 emandla ekuphehla ngenca yekwephuka kwemayunithi kanye nesiteleka sebasebenti bakaeskom lesingekho emtsetfweni.
tgt: gore naga e tsene mo kgatong ya borataro ya go tshaba ga mabone ke ka ntlha ya gore dijenereitara tse di fetlhang motlakase wa dimekawate di le 18 000 di robegile mme gape le badiri ba ba di baakanyang ba ne ba tsenela megwanto e e seng mo molaong ya go okelediwa megolo.

src: ngemuva kweminyaka lelishumi kunekushoda kwagezi, bantfu baseningizimu afrika bafanele kutfukutsela nekukhatsateka.
tgt: jaaka e setse e le sebaka sa go feta dingwaga di le lesome mabone a ntse a tshabetse ruri, selelo sa maaforika borwa mmogo le go tšhakgala ga bona go a tlhaloganyega.

src: ngetikhatsi letifanana naleti, kuvakala shengatsi lentfo ngeke ite iphele nyalo nanyalo.
tgt: fa seemo se le jaana, batho ba bona e le gore jaanong seno se feteletse.

src: nanome kucishwa kwagezi ngenhloso yekuwonga kubonakala shengatsi sekubi kakhulu, liciniso litsi sesitsatse tincumo letinyenti naletibalulekile tekulungisa lokushoda kwekuphakelwa kwagezi.
tgt: le fa go bonagala e kete go tshaba ga mabano go setse go feteletse, nnete ke gore go dikgato di le di ntsinyana tse re setseng re di tsere go rarabolola matsapa a tlhaelo ya mo tlakase.

src: lesikubeke embili lesitawucala ngako kutsi sikwente, kusimamisa luhlelo lwekuphakelwa kwagezi.
tgt: selo sa ntlha se se botlho kwa se re tshwanetseng go se dira ke go dira gore mabone a se tlhole a tshaba.

src: njengaloku loluhlelo seluvuka nekuphehlwa kwagezi sekubuyela esimeni, eskom utawukhona kutsi anciphise kucishwa kwagezi ngenhloso yekuwonga kube setigabeni letiphasi.
tgt: fa motlakase o busediwa sekeng le dijenereitara di baakanngwa, eskom e tla kgona go fokotsa dikgato tsa go tshaba ga mabone gore di nne kwa tlase.

src: lesivumelwane lokufinyelelwe kuso emkhatsini waeskom netinyonyana tebasebenti sitakwenta kutsi kukhonwe kulungisa loko lokumcoka kanye nekubuyisela esimeni kusebenta kwemayunithi langentiwe.
tgt: tumelano e e utlwanetsweng ke eskom le mekgatlho ya badiri e tla thusa gore tiro ya go baakanya dijenereitara tse di senyegileng go samaganwe le yona mmogo le go busetsa tirong diyuniti tse dingwe tsa tlamelo ya motlakase.

src: kuhanjiswa kwagezi lokusuka ecohora bassa emazambiki sekubuyiselwe esimeni futsi, lokwenta kutsi kungenteke 600 mw kugridi kanye neyunithi ye6 yasemedupi seyiyasebenta kusukela ngemgcibelo, lokukwengete lamanye ema720 mw.
tgt: megala ya motlakase e e tswang kwa cahora bassa kwa nageng ya mozambique e baakantswe, mme seno se okeditse motlakase wa rona ka dimekawate di le 600, e bile gape le yuniti ya borataro ya medupi le yona e buseditswe mo tirisong ka lamatlhatso o re tswang mo go ona, mme seno se okeditse motlakase wa rona ka dimekawate di le 720. diyuniti tse dingwe gape tsa tlamelo ya motlakase le tsona di tla busediwa tirong, mme seno se tla fokotsa tlhaelo e re lebaganeng le yona ya motlakase.

src: emayunithi langentiwe kulindzeleke kutsi asebente futsi, lokuyintfo letakwehlisa kakhulu umtfwalo wekushoda kwagezi lokukhona kwanyalo.
tgt: ka fa letlhakoreng le lengwe, ditheo tsa molao di samagane le namane e tona ya tiro ya go lwantshana le tshenyetso ya ka bomo, bogodu le bonweenwee kwa eskom go samagana le bogodu jo thulaganyo ya naga ya rona ya motlakase e tobaneng le bona.

src: ekugcineni, lokumcoka kutsi sidzinga kutsi singete kakhulu likhono lekwenta kugridi.
tgt: kwa bokhutlhong se se botlhokwa ke gore re tshwanetse re oketse mo tlakase o re nang le ona.

src: loku kutawudala kutsi eskom akhone kutsi atfole litfuba lekugcineka asesimeni lesibalulekile lesisebentako kanye nekwandzisa kwetsembeka kwetisetjentiswa takhe.
tgt: seno se tla thusa eskom gore e kgone go tlhokomela le go tsosolosa dithoto tsa yona tse di botlhokwa le go dira gore tiro ya yona e kgone go tshepagala.

src: loko kutawuphindza futsi kwakhe sivikelo sekutsi nanome emayunithi lamanyenti angephuka ngesikhatsi sinye, leminye imitfombolusito ingasetjentiswa.
tgt: seno se tla thusa le gore re nne le motlakase o o fetang le o re o tlhokang go re thusa gore fa re ka nna le matsapa a gore diyuniti tse dingwe di le mmalwa di senyege re bo re itse gore re na le motlakase o re ka o dirisang.

src: lesinye setinyatselo lengasitsatsa ngemnyaka wa2018 kwaba kuvusetela luhlelo lwekutsenga emandla lavusetelelwako.
tgt: e nngwe ya dikgato tsa ntlha tse ke di tsereng mo ngwageng wa 2018 e ne e le go fetola letsholo la dithendara tsa go reka motlakase wa go fetlhiwa ka ditsela tse dintšhwa.

src: kwengeta kulokutsengwa kwemandla lamasha ekuphehla ngekusebentisa loluhlelo, kwenyuka kwemkhawulo wemvume yemiklamo yekuphehla kwafinyelela kuma100 mw kusho kutsi batjalitimali labatimele imvume kute bakhe tisetjentiswa kute tifinyelele kulobungaka.
tgt: mo godimo ga go reka mo tlakase wa go fetlhiwa ka ditsela tse dintšhwa ka go dirisa letsholo leno, go ne ga okediwa gape le maemo a a tlhokang dilaesense fa o batla go tlhagisa motla kase mme diporojeke tse dintšhwa tse di tlhagisang motlakase di letleletswe gore ga di tlhoke dilaesense fa ba tlhagisa motlakase wa dimekawate di le 100, mme seno se raya gore bao ba agang mafelo a go tlhagisa motlakase o o sa feteng palo e e beilweng ga ba sa tlhoka go nna le dilaesense go dira jalo.

src: letingucuko letilula tivule emandla lamakhulu labegcinekile letako elutjalomali.
tgt: phetogonyana eno e buletse dipeeletso di thiba letsatsi tse di ka dirisiwang ka fa nageng.

src: eskom wente kutsi kube nemhlaba edvute netiteshi takhe temandla kute kutsi kube nelutjalomali lolutimele kumiklamo yemandla lavusetelelwako.
tgt: eskom e na le mabala gaufi le mo diteišeneng tsa bona tsa motlakase ao bao ba beeletsang mo motla kaseng wa go fetlhiwa ka ditsela tse dinšhwa tse di sa kgotlheleng tikologo ba ka a dirisang.

src: tindlela temadizayini setivele tiphotfuliwe kute kutsi kwentiwe ncono kusebenta kwemayunithi 1, 2 na3 asemedupi kantsi asachubeka kumayunithi 5 na6.
tgt: go setse go garetswe kgato ya go baakanya ka fao diyuniti tsa medupi di bong di tshwanetswe go agiwa ka gone gore yuniti ya bo 1, ya bo 2 le ya bo 3 di dire sentle mme go saletse fela yuniti ya bo 5 le ya bo 6. le fa tota dikgato tseno di le botlhokwa e bile di tla re tlela tse di molemo mo dikgweding tse di tlang, tsona di santse di le kgakala go ka samagana le matsapa a a re farafereng.

src: nanome lolokwentiwako kubalulekile futsi kutawutsela titselo kuletinyanga letitako, akukaneli kutsi kulungiseke lenkinga lesibukene nayo.
tgt: dibeke di le mmalwa tse di fetileng di re bontshitse gore re santse re tlhoka go dira go utlwagala ka bonako jo bo kgonagalang.

src: lokukhonjiswe ngulamaviki lambalwa lengcile kutsi sidzinga kutsi sente kakhulu futsi loko sikwente ngekuphutfuma.
tgt: ga go lebaka le le utlwagalang gore naga e tshwana le ya rona, e e phimphele tsweng ka bokgoni, badiri le dididiriswa, e tshwanetse go itshokela matsapa a go tlhaela motlakase.

src: asikho sizatfu sekutsi kungani live lelifanana naleletfu – lelinemakhono, emandla ekwenta kanye nemitfombolusito lesinawo – kufanele kutsi libe nekushoda kwagezi.
tgt: mo dibekeng di le mmalwa tse di fetileng, re ntse re mekamekana le tiro eno le ditona tse di ma leba mmogo le batlhanke di ba bagolo mo pusong re bontshana mekgwa e mentsi e e farologaneng e re ka e dirisang gore re kgone go kuka maoto mo go oke tseng motlakase wa rona.

src: umlayeto uyacaca: lesi akusiso sikhatsi sekusebenta njengalokwetayelekile.
tgt: molaetsa o tlhamaletse: ga re a tshwanela go dira dilo jaaka go tlwaelegile.

src: kudzingeka kutsi sitsatse sincumo ngesibindzi kute sente kucishwa kwegezi ngenhloso yekuwonga kube yintfo yasesikhatsi lesengca.
tgt: re tshwanetse go se boife fa re tsaya dikgato gore re kgone go fedisa ditiragalo tsa go tshaba ga motlakase.

src: nanome letinyatselo lesesititsatsile titawukwenta siciniseko sekutsi kuphakelwa ngekwetsembeka nekungabiti kwagezi esikhatsini lesitako, sesibuke kutsi ngutiphi letinye tinyatselo lesingatitsatsa nyalo kute kutsi sisondzete edvute leyo nhloso yetfu.
tgt: le fa e le gore dikgato tse jaanong re di tsereng di tla dira bonnete jwa gore mo isagong re nne le tlamelo ya motlakase e e tshepagalang e bile e sa je go le kalo ka fa potaneng, re ntse gape re lebelela gore ke dikgato dife tse dingwe tse re ka di tsayang gona jaanong gore seo re se batlang se goroge ka bonakonyana.

src: kungasikudzala sitawucedzisa umsebenti ngemininingwane kanye nekubonisana lokudzingekile kute siphotfule letinyatselo letichubekako.
tgt: e tla re mo nakong e e sa fediseng pelo ra konosetsa tiro e e tseneletseng le ya go batlana le maikutlo a baagi e leng seo se leng botlhokwa thata mo go gareleng dikgato tseno tsa tlaleletso.

src: sitawubeseke, ngekushesha, sesiyakhona kumemetela tinyatselo letiphelele kute sizuze inchubekelembili ngekushesha ekulweni nalenkinga yekucishwa kwagezi ngenhloso yekuwonga.
tgt: e tla re mo nakong e e sa fediseng pelo re itsise baagi gore ke dikgato dife tse di mosola tse re tla di tsayang gore re fitlhelele se re se batlang ka ponyo ya leitlho gore re kgone go khutlisa dikgato tsa go tshaba ga mabone.

src: indlela lensha yekulwa nenkhohlakalo itfola imiphumela lemihle vukuzenzele unnmaed kulwa nenkhohlakalo kudzinga sandla setepolitiki lesicinile kanye netikhungo, letitimele, letikhonako kulwa nebugebengu.
tgt: dikgato tse dintšhwa tsa go lwantshana le bonweenwee di nna le mosola vukuzenzele unnamed tiro ya go lwantshana le bonweenwee e tlhoka go enngwa nokeng ke maphata ka bobedi e leng maikemisetso a sepolotiki le setheo se se ikemetseng le se se itseng tiro ya sona mo go lwantshaneng le botlhokotsebe.

src: enkhulumeni yami yekucala yebunjalo belive, nga2018, ngenta sifungo sekutinikela kutsi ngigucule simo setenkhohlakalo eti khungweni tetfu ngiphi ndze futsi ngilwe neku khwabanisa nekubambisana ngenhloso lembi emkhakhe ni lotimele ngemandla ne nhloso lefananako.
tgt: fa ke ne ke neelana ka puo ya maemo a setšhaba (sona) lekgetlo la ntlha ka ngwaga wa 2018 ke ne ka dira maikano a gore ke tla dirisa maatla le mafolofolo a a tshwanang go lwantshana le bonweenwee mo ditheong tsa puso mmogo le go lwantsha na le bogwenegwene le go utlwanela ditlhwatlhwa tsa dithekiso mo ditheong tsa poraefete.

src: kusukela ngaleso sikhatsi, siloku sisebenta ngeku tikhandla kute sicinise siphindze futsi sisekele emaejensi etfu nalaha mbisana nawo lacinisekisa kutfotjelwa kwemtsetfo.
tgt: go tloga ka ona motsi oo re ntse re samagane le go ema nokeng ditheo tsa rona tsa molao le tse di dirang tiro e e tshwanang le eo.

src: sakhe luphiko lwete kuphenya kumtimba wavelonkhe wetekushu shisa kute kutsi libukane nenkhohlakalo lenemandla nekutsi inkantolo lekhetse kile yente luphiko lwete kuphenya lolukhetsekile (isiu) ikhone kuvumbulula kakhulu futsi kalula timali letintjontjiwe.
tgt: re ne ra tlhoma kantoro ya mokaedi wa dipatlisiso mo sethe ong sa bosekisi jwa naga (npa) gore e samagane le botlhokotsebe jo bogolo jwa bonweenwee mmogo le go tlhoma lekgotla la go sekela dikgetse tse di itlhophileng gore le kgone go thusa gore go nne bonolo go dira gore yuniti e e batlisisang dikgetse tse di itlhophileng (siu) e buse madi a a utswitsweng.

src: siphindze futsi sasita ngekwesekela nekunika imitfombolusito imitimba lebalulekile lelwa nebugebengu njengelu phiko lwekudla imphahla, luphiko lolukhetsekile lwetebugebengu beteku tsengisa kanye neluphiko lwekuphenya bugebengu lobuhamba embili, lolubitwa ngekutsi ngemahawks .
tgt: re eme gape nokeng le ditheo tse dingwe tse di lwantshanang le botlhoko tsebe tse di jaaka yuniti ya thopo ya dithoto, yuniti ya go lwantshana le dikgetse tse di itlhophileng tsa bosenyi mo dikgwebong mmogo le setheo sa dipatlisiso tsa melato e megolo ya botlho kwa ka go di neela kemono keng le didirisiwa tse di di tlhokang, se se tumileng thata ka leina la dihawks.

src: lemitamo inemiphumela lemihle.
tgt: dikgato tseno di setse di simolotse go nna le mosola.

src: ngekusebentisana netinhlaka letibalulekile eluhlelweni lwetebulu ngiswa kutebugebengu, luphiko lwetekuphenya selubhalise emacala enkhohlakalo langetulu kwalange20 kulomnyakati mali lophelile kwaphindze futsi kwaboshwa basolwa labange65.
tgt: ka ntlha ya go dirisana mmogo le ditheo tse di botlhokwa tsa twantsho ya bosenyi, kantoro eno ya mokaedi wa dipatlisiso e kgonne go tlhatlhela dikgetse di feta di le 20 tsa bonwee nwee mo ngwageng yo o fetileng wa matlole mmogo le go latofatsa batho ba le 65. melato eo ke e mmalwa ya 'ditiragalo tsa go goga puso ka nko' mmogo le dikgetse tse dingwe tse dikgolo tsa bonweenwee.

src: loku kufaka ekhatsi emacala lamanyenti 'ekubanjwa kwembuso ngabhongwane' kanye nalamanye emacala enkho hlakalo lamatima.
tgt: mo ngwageng yo o fetileng wa matlole yuniti ya thopo ya dithoto e ne ya rebolelwa taelo ya kgotlatshekelo ya gore e letleletswe go ka tswalela tiriso ya dithoto tsa boleng jo bo kanaka r5.4 bili one tse di nang le mofetsho wa ditiragalo tsa bonwee nwee, mo madi a le kana ka r70 milione a busitsweng ka go duelwa mo setheong sa pusetso ya matlole a bogodu.

src: kulomnyakatimali lophe lile, luphiko lwekudla imphahla lwatfola imiyalelo yekuvala emaakhawunti lalinganiselwa kutigidzi gidzi letir5.4 letiphatselene nemacala enkhohlakalo, kwatsi tigidzi letinger70 tafakwa esikhwameni semphahla yebugebengu levunjululiwe.
tgt: mo dingwageng di le robedi tse di fetileng, siu e setse e kgonne go busa madi le dithoto tse di neng di utswi tswe tse boleng jwa tsona bo ka dirang r2.6 bilione mmogo le go beela kwa thoko dikonteraka tsa dithendara tse di neng di utlwanetswe tse di ka dirang boleng jo bo kanaka r18 bilione.

src: kuleminyaka lesipho hlongo leyendlulile, isiu ivumbulule timali nempha hla leyenta tigidzigidzi letir2.6 yaphindze futsi yancamula emakontileka lenta tigidzigidzi letir18.
tgt: dikgetse tsotlhe di le kana ka 119 tse di ka dirang boleng jo bo kanaka r13 bilione di setse di kwadi sitswe ke siu kwa lekgotleng la go sekela dikgetse tse di itlhophileng.

src: inkhohlakalo licala lelima tima kakhulu kulishushisa.
tgt: bonweenwee ke tiragalo ya botlhokotsebe e go seng bonolo go samagana le yona semolaoditlhokotsebe tseno di tsaya matsapa gore go nne boima go ba rwesa melato.

src: babhebhetseli batikha ndla ngalokukhetsekile ekuvaleni imikhondvo yabo.
tgt: ba bula ditlamo tsa mouwane gore ka tsona ba kgone go fitlha ditiragalo tsa go tsamaisa madi ka bokhukhuntshwane, ba ntsha ba tsenya madi mo diakhaontong tsa dibanka tse dintsi tse di farologaneng, ba begela setheo sa lekgetho matlole a maaka, mme fa e le gore ke batlhankedi ba ba direlang puso, ba dira dikopo tsa dithendara ka go dirisa maina a ditsala tsa bona kgotsa a ba losika mme ba dirisa bona gore bona ba se tlhagelele.

src: bavula tinkampani letingasebenti tekutsi bafihle kuto imisebenti yabo lesolisako, njalonje bahambisa imali emkhatsini wemaakhawunti lama nyenti, betfule kubemtselo imalingena lengasiyo, futsi, basebenti bahulumende, basebentisa bangani nema lunga emndeni kutsi bafake ticelo temathenda kute kutsi bafihle kubandzakanyeka kwabo.
tgt: seno se raya gore fela jaaka le bona ba tsaya matsapa a ba a tsayang, le sepodisi le sona se tla tshwanela ke go tsaya matsapa a go tshwana le a bona.

src: nga2020, sasungula sikhungo ifusion centre lesimkhakhaminyenti saba sikhungo sekusebentela kute kutsi kubukwane nemacala ebugebengu lahamba embili, kufaka ekhatsi inkhohlakalo.
tgt: mo ngwageng wa 2020 re ne ra tlhoma setheo se se nang le batlhankedi go tswa kwa ditheong tse di farologaneng tsa molao e leng tikwatikwe ya ditirelo tse di golaganeng tsa go phuruphutsha bonwe enwee mme tikwatikwe eno e ne ya tshwanelwa ke go samagana le botlhokotsebe jo bogolo jwa go utswiwa ga madi, mmogo le jwa bonweenwee.

src: lesikhungo sihlanganisa emakhono ekuphenya etinhlaka tahulumende tekuvimbela bugebengu kanye netekuphepha kanye nalawo esikhungo sebunhloli kutetimali, lesi tfutfukisa tebunhloli kute kutsi tikhungo temtsetfo tiyisebentise eluphenyweni lwato.
tgt: tikwatikwe eno e na le batlhankedi ba ba diphatsa mo tirong ya diphuruphutso le pabalesego mo ditheong tsa puso tsa go lwantshana le botlhokotsebe mmogo le batlhankedi ba setheo sa go lwantshana le bogodu jwa ditšhelete, mme setheo seno se bokeletsa bopaki jwa bogodu jwa ma tlole mme o bo neye ditheo tsa molao gore ba bo dirise fa ba dira diphuruphutso.

src: eminyakeni lemibili kusukela kwasungulwa ifusion centre , indlela yaso lemkhakhaminyenti ‘yekulandzela imali’ ibe nemiphumela lemihle lemikhulu kakhulu.
tgt: mo dingwageng di le pedi nyana fela fa e sale tikwa tikwe eno e tlhomiwa, tiro ya yona ya go sola mosola batlhankedi go tswa kwa ditheong tse di farologaneng tsa molao go re tswetse mosola ka 'go nkgelela koo madi a isitsweng teng'.

src: kulomnyakatimali lophe lile, umsebenti wefusion centre usekele luphenyo lwenkhohlakalo neku khwabanisa lolunge276.
tgt: mo ngwageng yo o fetileng, tiro ya tikwatikwe ya ditirelo tse di golaganeng tsa go phuruphutsha bonweenwee e thusane le dipatlisiso di le 276 tsa ditiragalo tsa bogodu le bonweenwee.

src: tigidzi letilinganiselwa kuletinger659 tabuyi selwa kuhulumende ngekusebentisa kulondvo lota nekuvumbulula inzuzo yebugebengu.
tgt: madi a a balelwang go r659 milione a ne a busediwa puso ka go tsaya le go busetsa dithoto tsa bogodu.

src: kulinganiselwa kutigidzi letinger613 letavalwa lekusolwa kutsi tinzuzo tebugebengu.
tgt: dithoto tse di ka dirang r613 milione tse go belaelwang e le tsa bogodu go rebotswe taelo ya kgotlatshe kelo ya go tswalela tiriso ya dithoto tseo.

src: ifusion centre ekucaleni kwayo yasungulelwa kuphenya inkhohlakalo lephatselene nekutsengwa kwetintfo tecovid19 .
tgt: tikwatikwe ya ditirelo tse di golaganeng tsa go phuruphutsha bonweenwee kwa tshimologong e ne e tlhometswe go dira dipa tlisiso tsa bonweenwee mo dithendareng tse di amanang le covid .

src: manje umsebenti wayo sewukhulisiwe kute kutsi ufake ekhatsi kuphenya kushushunjiswa kwemali, kukhwabanisa, kulawula budlabha, kwesekela nge timali emaphekula kanye nalamanye emacala ebuge bengu labucayi.
tgt: jaanong tiro ya yona e setse e okeditswe mme jaanong e samagana gape le ditiragalo tsa go dira gore madi a bogodu e nne e kete ke a a bonweng ka ditsela tse di mo molaong, ditiragalo tsa bogodu, tsa go se dirise ditheo tsa puso ka tshwanelo, tsa go ema nokeng ka matlole digongwana tsa menolopuso mmogo le ditiragalo tse dingwe tsa botlhokotsebe jwa madi.

src: emahawks asandza kwendlala letinye tinchube kelembili letentiwe licembu lelilwa nenkhohlakalo, ifusion centre lebe yincenye yako.
tgt: mo malobanyaneng ba dihawks ba tlhagisitse tse dingwe tsa dikgatelopele tse ba di dirileng ka setlhopha sa tiro ya go lwantsha bonweenwee, mme setlho pha seno ke se sengwe sa ditlhopha tse e leng karolo ya tikwatikwe ya ditirelo tse di golaganeng tsa go phuru phutsha bonweenwee.

src: emkhatsini wemnya katimali wanga2019 nanga2022, kuboshwe basolwa labange554 baboshelwa inkhohlakalo, kwatsi laba142 babo balahlwa licala.
tgt: magareng ga ngwaga wa matlole wa 2019 le wa 2022, babelaelwa ba le 554 ba ba latofadiwang ka bonweenwee ba ne ba tshwariwa, mme mo go bona ba le 142 ba ne ba atlholelwa go ya kgolegelong jaaka bopaki bo bontsha gore ba molato.

src: lelinye lithulusi lebunhloli lelibalulekile kulucwa ningo lwendlela yekuphila lolwentiwe luphiko lwe kugcogcwa kwemtselo lwaseningizimu (yisars).
tgt: e nngwe ya dikarolo tse di botlhokwa tsa go lwantshana le bogodu jwa matlole ke dithulaganyo tsa go phu ruphutsa matshelo a batho ka fao ba itlhokomelang ka teng mme tsona di diriswa ke setheo sa tirelo ya lekgetho la aforika borwa (sars).

src: kulomnyaka lophelile, isars iphotfule lucwa ningo lwendlela yekuphila lolunge25 lolowenta tigidzi letinger450 kusombulula emagebe emkhatsini wemali lengenako ledzalulwako nendlela yekuphila yemuntfu.
tgt: mo ngwageng yo o fetileng sars e ne ya garela dithulaganyo tseno di le 25 tse boleng jwa tsona bo balelwang kwa godimo ga r450 milione maaitlhomo e le go rarabolola matsapa a a nnang teng ka ntlha ya fa botshelo jo ba bo tshelang bo sa tsamaisane le megolo e ba neileng bopaki jwa gore ke yona e ba nang le yona.

src: kuyacaca kutsi letinyatselo letitsetfwe ngulolulawulo kubuyisela emandla, likhono nekuncomeka kwetikhungo letilwa nekhohlakalo tinemphu mela lobonakalako lomuhle kakhulu.

src: caphela timphawu letisheshe tivele tamdlavuta wasebuntfwaneni more matshediso kungacapheli mdlavuta wase buntfwaneni kanye netinkhomba tawo kusho kutsi bantfwana labanyenti baseningizimu afrika ngesikhatsi batfolakala kutsi banalesifo sisuke sesisezi ngeni leliphakeme.

src: uma ngabe mdlavuta usheshe watfolakala wabese uyelashwa, ematfuba ekwelulama ngalokuphelele abasetulu.
tgt: fa bolwetse jwa kankere bo ka bonwa le go simololwa go alafiwa nako e santse e le teng, bolwetse jwa bona bo ka kgona go alafiwa gore bo folele ruri.

src: umchumanisi wenhlangano yaseningi zimu afrika yamdlavuta wasebuntfwaneni (ichoc) taryn seegers utsi ngekwati timphawu tamdlavuta kubantfu labancane, unga sita usindzise imphilo.
tgt: motlhankedi wa ditlhae letsano mo mokgatlong wa aforika borwa wa bolwetse jwa kankere mo baneng (choc) taryn seegers a re fa motho a itse matshwao a a tlwaelegileng a bolwetse jwa kankere mo baneng, motho yoo a ka kgona go thusa gore ngwana yo a nang le bona a se latlhegelwe ke botshelo jwa gagwe.

src: "timphawu netinkhomba kungaba matima kutibona emkhatsini wemaguludla, imitfubulela, timila kanye nekuntjintjantjintja kwemiva.
tgt: "ga go bonolo go bona matshwao a teng go nne ke setlwaedi gore bana ba a tle ba nne le dikukumpa, dintho, go oketsega mmele ka bonako kgotsa go felafela pelo.

src: nanoma kunjalo, kutfolakala kwato kubalule kile kakhulu," kusho yena.

src: ngekuya kwenhlangano yaseningizimu afrika yetamdlavuta (icansa), njalo ngemnyaka bantfwana baseningizimu afrika labatfolakala banamdla vuta basemkhatsini walabange800 kuya kulaba 1 000. nanoma kunjalo, lenhlangano ilinganisela ekutsini ihhafu yalaba ntfwana eningizimu afrika abatfolwa.
tgt: go ya ka mokgatlo wa naga ya aforika borwa wa merero ya bolwetse jwa kankere (cansa), ngwaga yo mongwe le yo mongwe go na le bana ba le magareng ga 800 le 1 000 ba go fitlhelwang gore ba na le bolwetse jwa kankere.

src: kwenta siciniseko sekutsi mdlavuta ubonwa masinyane, ichoc yenta tinhlelo tekucaphelisa emimangweni, itjela batali nebantfwana ngetimphawu letisheshe tibekhona teku caphelisa labafanele kutsi baticaphele.
tgt: le fa go le jalo, mokgatlo o no o re o dumela gore mo baneng botlhe ka fa nageng ya aforika borwa ba e leng gore ba na le bolwetse jwa kankere halofo ya bona ga go ke go itsiwe gore ba na le bona kgotsa jang.

src: lenhlangano yesekela bantfwana nebantfu labasha labanamdlavuta noma tifo tengati letisongela imphilo kanye nemindeni yabo.
tgt: go tsaya dikgato tsa go netefatsa gore bolwetse jwa kankere bo bonwa ka bonako nako e santse e le teng, choc e simolotse ka go diragatsa matsholo a go lemosa baagi mo metseng, e ruta batsadi le bana ka matshwao a ba tshwanetseng go a ela tlhoko nako e santse e le teng.

src: "sihlose kusheshe sisi bone lesifo bese siselapha ngemphumelelo.

src: nanoma ngunini, ichoc ingana kekela bantfwana nebantfu labasha labangetulu kwalaba1 500, ibe futsi yesekela ngekwetengcondvo nangekwetenhlalo imindeni lengetulu kwale1 500," kusho seegers.

src: kulomnyakatimali lophe lile, seegers utsi ichoc yakhona kutfula tinsita kubantfwana laba1 724, bantfu labasha laba553 kanye nebantfu labadzala laba2 232 ngetinhlelo tayo letingumgogodla.
tgt: setheo sa rona sa choc ka gang se ka kgona go amogela bana ba le 1 500 mo maokelong a sona, mmogo le go ema nokeng malapa a a feta a le 1 500 a a amegang ka thuso ya go thoba maikutlo le tlhaloganyo," seegers a rialo.

src: "tinsita tetfu tifaka ekhatsi kwesekelwa ngekwemiva ngesikhatsi basesebukene namdlavuta, kudvudvutwa, kunakekelwa kwaseku pheleni kwemphilo kanye nekwesekelwa uma sewu shonelwe," kusho seegers.

src: tincenye letitfutfukiswako nyalo sigaba semgwaco lomakhi lomitha (km) la19 losuka ecato ridge ufike edarda nelles, lowatiwa ngekutsi ngumgwaco iumlaas; sigaba semgwaco lesi20.6 km losuka edardanelles inter change kuya elynnfield park; kanye nesigaba semgwaco lesi30km losuka elynnfield park uye eashburton inter change.
tgt: dikarolo tse di atoloswang ga jaana ke ya dikhilomitara di le 19 e e gogang go tswa kwa cato ridge go leba kwa dardanelles, e e itsegeng thata ka gore ke umlaas road; karolo ya dikhilomitara di le 26.6 e e tswang kwa dardane lles interchange go leba kwa lynnfield park; mmogo le karolo ya dikhilomitara di le 30 go tswa kwa lynnfield park go leba kwa ashburton interchange.

src: matekane utsi isip2 itawukhulisa lomgwaco weti gitjelwa newetekutfutswa kwemphahla losemkhatsini kwemahabhu etimboni la mcoka aseningizimu afrika, itawutfutfukisa kufinyelela kutinsita tekuhanjiswa nekunge niswa kwemphahla letisethekwini futsi itawu khuphula lizinga lekusebenta ngendlela lekahle kule phaseji.

src: ungete ngekutsi lomklamo uyincenye yeluhlelo lwavelonkhe lwentfu tfuko lwemnyaka we2030 neluhlelo lolukhulu letekutfutsa lwemnyaka we2050 futsi usekela luhlelo lwahulumende lwekwakha kabusha nele kuvuselela umnotfo.

src: tjwala bungalimata imphilo yemntfwana wakho asengakatalwa vukuzenzele unnamed bomake labakhulelwe banemsebenti weku tivikela banganatsi tjwala ngoba bungabanga sifo lesitsikameta kukhula kwemntfwana.

src: loku kushiwo lisekela lendvuna yetekufutfukisa tenhlalo, hendrietta bogo panezulu, losandza kucala luhlelo lwekulwa nesifo i999 foetal alcohol spectrum disorder (ifasd).
tgt: seno ke go ya ka motlatsatona wa tlhabololo ya loago, hendrietta bogopanezulu, yo mo malobanyaneng ka ura ya bo robongwe ka letsatsi la bo robongwe mo kgwedi ng ya bo robongwe a neng a thankgolola letsholo la go buisana le baagi la malwetse a a farologaneng mo maseanya neng a a iseng a belegwe a a tlhodiwang ke go itshiela ga bomme ba ba ithweleng (999 fasd).

src: inhloso yalomkhankhaso kugcugcutela imimango kutsi isite kuvikela bantfwana lebasengakabelekwa ngekufundzisa bantfu, kakhulu bomake labasakhona kubeleka, mayelana nebu ngoti bekunatsa tjwala ube ukhulelwe noma usamu nyisa.
tgt: maitlhomo a letsholo leno ke go rotloetsa baagi gore ba sireletse maseanyana ano a a iseng a belegwe ka go ruta baagi ka dikotsi tsa go itshiela o le mo mmeleng kgotsa o le motsetse, segolobogolo batho ba bomme ba mebele ya bona e setseng e ka kgona go ka nna le bana.

src: "kumcoka kutsi bonkhe bomake labakhulelwe nalabo labanesifiso sekutala bantfwana labaphile kahle bayekele kunatsa tjwala.
tgt: "go botlhokwa thata gore basadi ba ba leng mo mmeleng kgotsa ba ba batlang go belega bana ba ba senang matsapa gore ba se itshiele.

src: umonakalo lobangwa yifasd uba wemphilo yonkhe futsi awubuyiseleki emuva, futsi bantfwana labatalwa nalokugula baba netinkinga tasemtimbeni netasengco ndvweni," kwasho lisekela lendvuna bogopanezulu emcimbini wekwetfulwa kwaloluhlelo.
tgt: seo fasd e se dirang mo maseanyaneng ano ke setlhogo se se nnelang ruri mo go bona seo se senang pheko, mme bana ba ba belegwang ba na le matsapa ano a a tle a ame mebele ya bona kgotsa ditlhaloganyo tsa bona," motlatsatona bogopanezulu o tlhalositse jalo fa go ne go thankgololwa letsholo leno.

src: wangeta ngekutsi iningi zimu afrika yatiwa ngekuba nenkinga yekunatsa tjwala, lelive libalwa njengalamanye lamabi lahamba embili emhlabeni ngenca yemazinga alo ekunatsa tjwala.
tgt: o tlaleleditse gape le ka gore aforika borwa e itsege thata ka gore ke naga e e ratang bojalwa mo go maswe, mo e tsewang e le e nngwe ya dinaga tse di tlompunye ditseng tlhogo mo nkgong.

src: lisekela lendvuna bogopanezulu usandza kuhambela tincenye letehlukahlukene talelive letfu, afundzisa bomake mayelana nebungoti bekunatsa tjwala bakhulelwe njengencenye yemkhankaso we999 fasd.
tgt: mo go diragatseng letsholo la 999 fasd mo malobanyaneng, motlatsatona bogopanezulu o ne a jela nala dikarolo di le mmalwa tsa ka fa nageng, mo a neng a lemosa batho ba bomme ka dikotsi tsa go itshiela o le mo mmeleng.

src: lesikhatsi aseboitekong erustenburg enyakatfo nshonalanga, watjela takhamuti kutsi lizinga leku setjentiswa kabi kwetjwala emalokishini liyesabeka.
tgt: fa a ne a le kwa lekeišeneng la boitekong kwa rustenburg mo porofenseng ya bokone bophirima, o ne a bolelela baagi ba foo gore ka fao ba tsuntsunyetsang bojalwa ka teng mo lefelong leo go a tshosa.

src: make lonetinyanga letine akhulelwe lohlala eboite kong, basetsane tlalang (28), lobekahambele lomunye walemikhankaso, utse wayekela futsi wagcina ngci kunatsa emva kwekutfola kutsi ukhulelwe futsi watsi sewuhambela emaseshini asemtfolamphilo elwatiso newesikhatsi lesandvulela kubeleka.
tgt: lekgarebe la kwa boitekong la dingwaga di le 28, le le nang le sebaka sa dikgwedi di le nne le ithwele e bong basetsana tlalang, ke yo mongwe wa batho ba ba neng ba le teng mo letsholong leno mme o ne a tlhalosa gore ene o sele a emisa go itshiela morago ga gore a itse gore o ithwele mme o ntse a ya tleleniking go tlhatlhobiwa le go tlhatlhelelwa ka tshedimosetso ya go mo bula matlho.

src: uncusa labanye bomake labakhulelwe kutsi bayekele leso sikhatsi kunatsa tjwala nekusebentisa tidzakwamiva.
tgt: o dirile boikuelo mo basading ba bangwe ba le bona ba ithweleng gore ba emise go itshiela le go dirisa diritibatsi ka ona motsotso oo.

src: umshikashika wekubuyisa ubuntfu eningizimu afrika vukuzenzele unnamed mhla ti12 inyoni 1977, ste phen bantfu biko washona agcinwe maphoyisa ejele lelatiwa ngepretoria central prison.
tgt: go kgaratlhela go aga naga ya aforika borwa e e neelang ditshwanelo tsa botho seriti vukuzenzele unnamed ka la bo 12 lwetse 1977, stephen bantu biko o ne a bolawa a tswaletswe kwa kgolegelong ya pretoria central prison.

src: sitfunti sebuntfu, leku simiso lesihamba embili kulobushoshovu bakhe bekubuyisa sitfunti semuntfu lomnyama, sacekelwa phasi.
tgt: o bolailwe ka polao e e tlhokang seriti, e leng sona selo se se neng se tlhotlheletsa mogopolo wa gagwe wa gore bathobantsho ba bule matlho ba itse gore le bona ke batho.

src: ngekwemagama emmeli wemndeni wakhe sir sydney kentridge, "kushona kwakhe bekubuhlungu kakhulu futsi bekayedvwa ashonela emethini lephasi esemendeni yelijele."
tgt: fa re dirisa mafoko a rramolao yo e neng e le mmueledi wa lapa la gagwe e bong rre sydney kentridge, o ne a tlhalosa a re "o tlhokafetse setlhogo a le esi a kudupane mo metsheng o o adilweng mo fulurung ya matlapa ka fa teng ga kamotshana ya kgolegelo".

src: kutawuhlala kuyintfo lebanga lusizi lolukhulu emva kwayo yonkhe leminyaka leyengcile, kukhumbula kutsi steve biko bakaneminyaka le30 kuphela uma ashona.
tgt: le jaanong morago ga dingwaga tseno tsotlhe e santse e le kutlobotlhoko e e seng kana ka sepe fa re gopola gore kana steve biko o ne a na fela le dingwaga di le 30 fa a ne a bolawa.

src: wabulawa asengakafiki esicongweni semphilo yakhe ngilabo bebasaba emandla ekubona imibono yakhe lesetulu yekutikhulula kanye nemitamo yekufaka kumuntfu lomnyama kutitsandza nekuba nesitfunti emadvodzeni nakubomake besive lesinsundvu.
tgt: o ne a isiwa maotwanahunyela a santse a le monnye ke bao ba neng ba boifa gore megopolo ya gagwe e e neng e na le maatla e bile e ratega e e ka ga boipuso jwa mothomontsho le matsapa a gagwe a go dira gore monna wa mothomontsho le mosadi wa mothomontsho ba ipele ka seo e leng sona le go nna le seriti gonne seno se ne se ba tshosa mo go maswe.

src: azange akhone kubona ekuphileni kwakhe loko lokubitwa ngekutsi ‘ngumklomelo lokhatimu lako", lekukubona buntfu bangemphela.
tgt: o tlhokafetse a ise a bone seo a neng a se bitsa ‘bokamoso jo bo benyang’, se diragala mo batho ba tshelang jaaka batho.

src: abhala ngalomcondvo, kwadvuma kutsi watsi: "ngekuhamba kwesikhatsi sitawukhona kupha iningizimu afrika sipho lesikhulu kunato tonkhe – kukhulisa sitfunti sebuntfu."
tgt: fa a ne a kwala ka kgopolo eno o ne a re: "go tla goroga letsatsi leo re tla neelang aforika borwa mpho ya go di phala tsotlhe go rwesa baagi ba naga seriti.

src: uma sincoba sitfola inkhu luleko yetfu ngemnyaka we1994, besivisisa kutsi lilungelo lekuvota liyincenye leyodvwa yemzabalazo wetfu wekutfola sitfunti sebuntfu.
tgt: "fa re ne re fenya kgololesego ya rona mo ngwageng wa 1994, re ne re itse sentle gore go fenya tshwanelo ya go letlelelwa gore le rona re nne le seabe mo ditlhophong e ne e le karolonyana e le nnye fela ya go fenya kgaratlhelo ya rona ya go nna le seriti.

src: eminyakeni lemashumi lamabili nesiphohlongo singene kuntsandvoye linyenti, sihlangabetene netinseyeya letinyenti, letifana nebuphuya, kuswelakala kwemisebenti nekungalingani.
tgt: jaanong temokerasi ya rona e setse e na le dingwaga di le 28, mme re santse re tobane le dikgwetlho tse dintsi tse di jaaka tshokolo, botlhokatiro le go se lekane re se meno.

src: ngenca yaloko, sivamise kunga boni kutsi sisuka khashane kanganani kute sikhone kufeza timiso letisisekelo semtsetfosisekelo wetfu futsi letichumanisa imicondvo netifundziso tasteve biko.
tgt: ka ntlha ya seno, re iphitlhela go le gantsi re sa bone le gore ko re tswang go kgakala jang mo go diragatseng dintlha tse di botlhokwa tseo molaotheo wa naga ya rona o ikageletseng mo godimo ga tsona tseo di ikaegileng ka megopolo le dithuto tsa ga steve biko.

src: ngemnyaka we1997, umbuso lobewungenalu velo wabulala lomunye umholi walelive lakitsi lobekatse mbisa kakhulu ngekumncisha kudla, emanti kanye nekwelashwa lobe kakudzinga kakhulu ngenca yekushaywa kabuhlungu ngemaphoyisa elubandlu lulo.
tgt: ka ngwaga wa 1977, puso e e setlhogo e e neng e busa ka nako eo e ne ya bolaya o mongwe wa baeteledipele ba naga ya rona ba e neng e le baganka ka go mo tima dijo, metsi le ditirelo tsa kalafi ya tshoganyetso tse a neng a di tlhoka ka nako eo ka ntlha ya fa sepodisi sa puso ya tlhaolele se ne se mo ntshitse dikgobalo tse di masisi fa se ne se mo keteka.

src: emva kweminyaka lemashumi lamabili, sincumo senkantolo semnyaka we1997, inkantolo yemtsetfosisekelo yatsi kuphumelelisa emalungelo lasisekelo awo wonkhe umuntfu nekutfola ema lungelo abo etemnotfo kuluphawu lwemmango wentsandvoyelinyenti loluhlose kubuyisela sitfunti lesilahlekile.
tgt: morago ga dingwaga di le 20, ka ngwaga wa 1997 kgotlatshekelo ya molaotheo e ne ya rebola katlholo e e reng go diragatsa ditshwanelo tse di botlhokwa tsa moagi yo mongwe le yo mongwe mmogo le go kgaratlhela ditshwa nelo tsa bona mo botshelong le mo go itireleng letseno ke selo se se botlhokwa thata mo setšhabeng seo se itsayang e le se se dumelang mo temokerasing seo maitlhomo a sona e leng go busetsa seriti sa bao ba latlhegetsweng ke seriti sa bona.

src: namuhla eningizimu afrika, siyachubeka kuse bentela kuphumelelisa emalungelo lasisekelo awo wonkhe umuntfu waseningizimu afrika kute baphile imphilo lesezingeni lenge nato tifo, indlala nekuswela.
tgt: gompieno ka fa nageng ya aforika borwa, re samagane le go dira gore re diragatse ditshwanelo tse di botlhokwa tsa moaforika borwa mongwe le mongwe gore ba kgone go tshela botshelo jo bo nang le maemo jo bo senang malwetselwetse, jo bo senang khuma nego le jo bo senang tshokolo.

src: imibuso yentsandvoye linyenti lelandzelanako isebentise imitsetfomigomo leletsa sitfunti sebantfu balelive lebesilahlekile ngekubanika imfundvo, kunakekelwa kwetemphilo, tindlu kanye netinsita letisi sekelo.
tgt: ditheo tsa temokerasi di atlegile mo go diragatseng dipholisi tsa go busetsa seriti sa bao ba neng ba latlhegetswe ke seriti bao e leng bona batho ba bantsi ka fa nageng eno ka go ba isa sekolong, go ba abela ditirelo tsa kalafo, go ba agela dintlo le go ba tlamela ka ditirelo tse di botlhokwa.

src: namuhla eningizimu afrika, kutfola imfundvo lesezingeni kulilungelo lelisisekelo.
tgt: gompieno ka fa nageng ya aforika borwa ke tshwanelo e e botlhokwa ya motho mongwe le mongwe go iponela maemo a thuto e e nang le seriti.

src: hulumende utjale timali kumfundvo legcile ekukhuliseni kahle bantfwana, ekusekeleni imiphumela yetifundvo ebantfwaneni balelive lakitsi labasesebancane, futsi kusita ummango ngeluhlelo leku phakela bantfwana kudla etikolweni kucinisekisa kutsi bafundzi labasesebancane batfola imiphumela lesetulu.
tgt: puso e dira dipeeletso mo thutong ya bomapimpana (ecd), go dira gore bana ba nne le bokgoni jwa go ithuta ba sa le bannye, mmogo le go ba rola boima ba tshokolo ka sekema sa go fepa bana ba sekolo go dira gore bana bano ba kgone go tobana fela le dibuka tsa bona gore ba kgone go ntsha dipholo tse dintle tse ba ka di kgonang.

src: ngalesikimu savelonkhe selusito lwetimali kuba fundzi nangaletinye tinhlobo telusito lwahulumende, tinkhulungwane tebantfu labasha baseningizimu afrika labavela eminde nini lephuyile bakhonile kuba bodokotela, bammeli, bothishela, bososayensi, emaathizeni nabosomabhi zinisi.
tgt: ka ntlha ya sekema sa naga sa go thusa baithuti ba ditheo tsa thuto e kgolwane ka ma tlole a go ya sekolong mmogo le ka ntlha ya tse dingwe tsa dikgato tse dintsinyana tse di farologaneng tse puso e di tsayang, bašwa ba maaforika borwa ba le bantsi go tswa kwa malapeng a a dikobodikhu tshwane ba kgonne go ka nna dingaka, batlhankedi ba molao, barutabana, borasaense, badiri ba ditiro tsa diatla le baitshimololedi ba dikgwebo.

src: hulumende usekela takhamuti letibutsakatsaka ngekusebentisa tinhlelo tekusita emakhaya laphuyile futsi iniketa ematfuba emisebenti ngaletinhlelo tahulumende tekucasha bantfu labanengi.
tgt: puso e thusa baagi ba naga eno ba ba sokolang le ba ba tlhokang ka letsholo la megolo ya gore ba kgone go iphedisa mmogo le ka go ba naya ditiro ka go ba thapa mo matsholong a go direla setšhaba.

src: kuleningizimu afrika lebeyicindzetela leyabulala steve biko, bekute kukhu luma ngekukhululeka kantsi kuba sishoshovi kutepolitiki bekuholela ekutseni uboshwe ngaphandle kwekushushiswa noma ubulawe.
tgt: mo pusong ya aforika borwa wa tlhaolele eo e bolaileng steve biko, batho ba ne ba tseetswe ditshwanelo tsa go ntsha maikutlo a bona mo phasala tseng e bile go tsaya karolo mo dipolotiking e ne e le sebe se sekgolo se se ka dirang gore o tshwariwe kgotsa o diriwe selo se se bosula le go feta.

src: namuhla eningizimu afrika, bantfu labasha labaneminyaka lelingana naleyo bekanayo steve biko noma lemincane kunaleyo bahamba embili kutebu shoshovi betintfo leti sedvute nabo, futsi bayakhona kutihlela kahle ngekukhululeka ngaphandle kwekuhlukunyetwa noma kwekudzingiswa.
tgt: mo nageng ya aforika borwa gompieno bašwa ba e leng bankane ba steve biko kgotsa ba bannye go feta ka fao a neng a le ba kgona go lwela ditshwa nelo tsa bona mo go seo ba dumelang gore se botlhokwa, ba kgona go simolola mekga tlho ntle le go boifa kgotsa go tshaba gore ba ka kgariediwa kgotsa ba kobiwa mo ba nnang teng.

src: kukhu luma nekuhlanganyela ngekukhululeka, lilungelo lekubhikisha kanye nelilungelo lekulingana ngembi kwemtsetfo ku yalandzelwa kubo bonkhe bantfu.
tgt: ditshwanelo tsa go ntsha maikutlo a gago mo phasalatseng le go tsenela mokgatlo mongwe le mongwe, ditshwanelo tsa go bolotsa megwanto le ditshwanelo tsa go tshwariwa ka go tshwana mo pele ga matlho a molao ke ditshwanelo tseo di sireleditsweng gore di tswele batho botlhe molemo.

src: sisive, sihambe libanga lelidze kute siphumelele kutfola sitfunti sebuntfu, lekusimiso besihlonishwa ngusteve biko.
tgt: re le naga re tswa kgakala mo go diragatseng kgang ya go busetsa batho seriti, e leng selo se steve biko a neng a beile pelo ya gagwe thata mo go sona.

src: kungasebenti, kungabi nendlu, nagezi noma emanti lahambako, kungabi nemhlaba, kungabi nemakhono noma ematfuba, tigidzi tebantfu baseningizimu afrika basengakayitfoli imphilo lebafuna kuyi phila.
tgt: matshelo a le dimilione tsa maaforika borwa a santse a tshwana le a mo nakong e e fetileng jaaka ba retelelwa ke go tshela botshelo jo ba neng ba ipatlela bona jo bo ba tshwanetseng ka ntlha ya fa ba sena ditiro, dintlo, motlakase kgotsa metsi a dipompo, jaaka ba sena lefatshe, bokgoni kgotsa ditšhono.

src: kungako hulu mende asebentisana nebalingani betemnotfo kute kwakhiwe umnotfo lofaka wonkhe umuntfu, kwakhiwe ematfuba emisebenti, kuncedvwe emabhizinisi aphumelele futsi kuliwe nebuphuya nendlala.
tgt: ke ka ntlha ya seno re bonang puso e ntse e tshwarisane tiro eno le badirisanimmogo mo mererong ya loago go dira gore re nne le ikonomi e botlhe ba nang le seabe mo go yona, e e tla kgonang go tlhola ditiro, go dira gore dikgwebo di ntshe ga tshwene mmogo le go lwantshana le tshokolo le khumanego.

src: uma sibuka kubaluleka kwemlandvo nemphilo yasteve biko, siya phindza futsi senta lubito lolunemandla lekutsi bantfu kube ngibo lebakha indlela leya kunkhululeko yabo.
tgt: fa re tsaya tsiya lefa leo steve biko a re sietseng lona mo botshelong jwa gagwe, re ka ikgopotsa boikuelo jo a neng a bo dira jwa gore batho e tshwanetse e nne bona ba ba itseelang ditshwetso mo matshelong a bona ka tokologo e ba batlang go e bona.

src: lolubito lumcoka nyalo njengoba belumcoka nangaleso sikhatsi.
tgt: boikuelo jono le go na jaanong bo santse bo le botlhokwa fela jaaka bo ne bo le mo nakong e e fetileng.

src: kufuneka sigcile ekulweni netinseyeya tetfu kute sibe ngummango lokhululekile ngaloku phelele nalonekulingana.
tgt: re tshwanetse go tsepamisa mogopolo thata mo go rarabololeng dikgwetlho tse re tobaneng le tsona gore re kgone go nna le setšhaba se tokologo le tekatekano e leng dilo tsa boammaruri mo go sona.

src: luhlelo lwekunika bahlukunyetwa emandla lubuyisa litsemba owen mngadi luhlelo lasethohoya ndou lwekunika bahlu kunyetwa emandla (itvep) lufuna kubuyisa litsemba nekutitsemba kuluhlelo lwetebulungiswa ngekusebentisa tinyatselo talo letinemandla letihlose kusita labo labasindzile kuludlame lolumayelana netebulili (igbv) nasekudlwengulweni ngekubanika tinsita tetengco ndvo.
tgt: letsholo la go matlafatsa batswasetlhabelo le dira gore batho ba nne le tsholofelo owen mngadi letsholo la go matlafatsa batswasetlhabelo kwa thohoyandou (tvep) le leka ka natla go dira gore baagi ba boe ba nne le tshepo mo dikgatong tsa molao tsa phimolakeledi ka go diragatsa matsholo a yona a a tseneletseng ao maitlhomo a ona e leng go tswa thuso batswasetlhabelo ba ba fetileng mo mathateng a ditiragalo tsa go bogisa basadi (gbv) le a go betelelwa ka go ba tlamela ka ditirelo tsa go ba thoba maikutlo le tsa go fodisa tlhaloganyo.

src: letvep leyacalwa elimpo po eminyakeni lema20 leye ngcile, isebentela etibhedlela itshilidzini nedonald fraser letingaphasi kwamasipala wasekhaya ithulamela.
tgt: letsholo leno le le simolotsweng kwa porofenseng ya limpopo le le nang le sebaka sa dingwaga di le 20 le teng kwa sepetlele sa tshilidzini le kwa sepetlele sa donald frasermo mo masepaleng wa selegae wa thulamela.

src: libamba lemcondzisi waloluhlelo fhatuwani manthada utsi loluhlelo luhlose kufaka indlela yekubuka tintfo lengavumeli nakancane kutsi kube nekuhlukunyetwa ngekwemacansi, ngekwegbv kanye nekwebantfwana kuletakhamuti tasethohoyandou, ngoba kuliciniso lelimsulwa kutsi loluhlobo lwemacala ayenteka kulendzawo.
tgt: mokaedi wa namaotshware, fhatuwani manthada, a re mai tlhomo a letsholo leno ke go dira gore baagi botlhe ba thohoyandou ba se tlhole ba itshokela ditiro tse dintsintsi tsa go sotla batho ba bangwe ka thobalano, go bogisa basadi mmogo le go bogisa bana, segolobogolo jang jaaka ditiragalo tseno e le tsona tse di renang mo lefelong leno.

src: utsi esikhatsini lesengci le, lubalobalo lwemacala beluvamise kukhomba kutsi bewamanengi emacala ekudlwengula ethohoyandou, kodvwa itvep ibe neligalelo lelikhulu ekuletseni lwatiso nekunika bantfu tinsita tekwelulekwa ngekuhlukumeteka kute kuliwe nalomkhuba lomubi.
tgt: o tlhalositse gore mo nakong e e fetileng dipalopalo di ne di bontsha gore dikgetse tsa petelelo ke tsona tse di neng di le kwa godimo mo thohoyandou, mme fa e sale letsholo leno la tvep le simolola go na le kgatelopele e e namatshang fa go tla mo go fokotseng ditiragalo tseno jaaka le lemosa baagi ka ditiragalo tseno mmogo le go tlamela batswasetlhabelo ka ditirelo tsa go ba thoba maikutlo.

src: njengoba umhlaba wonkhe utawube ubuke lomkhankhaso wetinsuku leti16 tebushoshovi bekucedza ludlame lolubhekiswe kubomake nasebantfwaneni kusuka mhla ti25 lweti kuya kumhla ti10 ingongoni, manthada utsi loluhlelo lunelisekile ngaloku leselikwentile lekukugcugcutela takhamuti kutsi tiwavisise emalungelo ato nekutsi tibike uma kwenteka emacala.
tgt: jaaka mo lefatsheng go tla bo go ketekiwa letsholo la matsatsing a le 16 la go ema kgatlhanong le tirisodikgoka mo basading le mo baneng go simolola ka la bo 25 ngwanaitseele go fitlha ka la bo 10 sedimonthole, manthada a re o kgotsofatswa ke seo se setseng se dirilwe mo letsholong leno jaaka le rutile baagi gore ba itsi ditshwa nelo tsa bona le go ba rotloetsa go tshwarisa ditlhokotsebe tse di dirang melato eno.

src: "letvep itfola bahlukunye twa beludlame lwasekhaya labasemkhatsini kwe80 ne100 njalo ngenyanga, bese kuba macala ekudlwengulwa la45 kuya ku50 labikwa njalo ngenyanga," kusho manthada.
tgt: "mo kgweding e nngwe le e nngwe tvep e amogela batho ba le magareng ga ba le 80 le ba le 100 ba e leng batswasetlhabelo ba tirisodikgoka ya batho ba ba amanang, mme ka fa letlhakoreng le lengwe kgwedi e nngwe le e nngwe go bulwa dikgetse tsa petelelo di le magareng ga di le 45 go fitlha go di le 50," manthada o tlhalositse jalo.

src: sikhungo lesisodvwa lesiphetse konkhe kwalolu lelo siniketa tinsita letehluka hlukene kubahlukunye twa, letifaka ekhatsi lusito lwetemtsetfo, kuvikeleka kwebahlukunyetwa kulabo lababahlukumetako, kula ndzelela emacala lasenkantolo, kwelulekwa nekuniketwa emandla ngekusebentisa luhlelo lwekutfutfukisa emakhono, ngaloko bahlukunyetwa batfola litfuba lekucala kabusha.
tgt: lefelo la ditirelontsi la letsholo leno le tlamela batswasetlhabelo ka ditirelo tse dintsi tse di farologaneng tse ba di tlhokang, mmogo le tsa go ba thapela babueledi, tsa go sireletsa batswasetlhabelo gore ditlhokotsebe di se tswelele go ba tshosetsa, ditirelo tsa go disa dikgetse tseno fa di le kwa kgotla tshekelo, ditirelo tsa go ba thoba maikutlo le go ba tlhatlheleka ka kitso e e rileng go tshwana le go ba tlhatlhelela ka bokgoni, mme seno se thusa batswasetlhabelo gore ba kgone go ikemela mo botshelong ntle le go thusiwa ke bao ba neng ba ba bogisa.

src: manthada utsi letvep isebenta ngekubambisana nebetemisebenti yetemapho yisa aseningizimu afrika, litiko letemphilo kanye nelekutfutfukiswa kwemma ngo kute kuvikelwe kutsi bahlukunyetwa bangaphindzi bahlukumeteke kwesibili ngalesikhatsi bavula emacala.
tgt: manthada a re mo go direng gore batswasetlhabelo ba se kgopisiwe lekgetlo la bobedi mo moweng, tvep e tshwarisane tiro le tirelo ya sepodisi sa aforika borwa (saps), lefapha la boitekanelo mmogo le lefapha la tlhabololo ya loago.

src: "emacaleni ekudlwengula, basebenti betemphilo nema phoyisa beta etikhungweni tetvep kutosita bahlukunye twa bavule emacala bavulele labo lababahlukumetako futsi, babanika tinsita tekwelulekwa," usho njalo.
tgt: "mo dikgetseng tse di amanang le petelelo, batlhankedi ba lephata la maokelo mmogo le ba sepodisi ba etela lefelo la tvep le motswasetlhabelo a tshabetseng kwa go lona go tla go bula kgetse kgatlhanong le setlhokotsebe sa tiro eo mmogo le go tla go thoba motswasetlhabelo maikutlo," o tlhalositse jalo.

src: itvep ihlalisa labo labahlukumetekile kute kufike etinsukwini leti14, kodvwake, loluhlelo lwekuhlaliswa lungalulwa emacaleni lafaka umndeni wonkhe noma bantfwana.
tgt: mafelo a tvep a amogela batswasetlhabelo sebaka sa matsatsi a le 14, mme le fa go le jalo, a kgona go amogela motho sebaka sa matsatsi a a fetang ano segolo jang fa e le gore lapa lotlhe le tshabetse koo kgotsa fa e le gore motswasetlhabelo yo a tshabetseng koo ke ngwana.

src: "sineyunithi yekunika emandla lehamba icocisana nebantfu futsi ibafundzise mayelana nemalungelo abo.
